ype":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zssdhrz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心素材优先库："}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t4qgzdt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t4qgzdt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w3kfnu3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w3kfnu3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f08uhgg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f08uhgg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钱伟长（中国力学之父）：必须作为核心论据或升华点。重点使用其“九一八事变后，物理仅15分的他毅然弃文从理，只为‘科学救国’”的转折。体现“个人命运与国家命运的同频共振”，以此替换老旧的“范仲淹”、“岳飞”等素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-47qm082","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-47qm082","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3b8fchq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3b8fchq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西西弗斯（加缪笔下的荒诞英雄）：必须作为核心意象。重点描写他推石上山的徒劳与坚持，引用“登上顶峰的斗争本身足以充实人的心灵”。用以论证“在无意义的生活中构建意义”、“过程即意义”，以此替换老旧的“海伦·凯勒”、“张海迪”等素材。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5hhtrtp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ny4=","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5hhtrtp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ov6oum0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ov6oum0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"古典底蕴与化用："}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-looni68","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-looni68","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e5seeb3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e5seeb3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o11is13","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o11is13","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至少自然嵌入2–3条下面提供的的典故、文章(不必引用原文，文章总结、提炼亦可)、诗词名句、电影，并保证与论证逻辑紧密相关。"}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fdd9c4s","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fdd9c4s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tkqhfgz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tkqhfgz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kpho63o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kpho63o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《尚书》五福：寿、福、康宁、攸好德、考终命"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mu6duav","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mu6duav","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ncqup9n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ncqup9n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鲁迅：无穷的远方，无数的人们，都与我相关。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0b3utso","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0b3utso","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ypnofcg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ypnofcg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"投之亡地然后存，陷之死地然后生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-llc7oy8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-llc7oy8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5wkc3s7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5wkc3s7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2zz4suv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2zz4suv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-twv2ab5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-twv2ab5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"路遥《平凡的世界》当一个人集中地凝视着自己的不幸时，他就很难想象别人的苦难。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m8gn81b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m8gn81b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-68nul07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-68nul07","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小敌之坚，大敌之擒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-20gbdvd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-20gbdvd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g5p1e7o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g5p1e7o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小人肥口，君子肥身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rfm893v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rfm893v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-997phe0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-997phe0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我生本无乡，心安是归处。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hro5fmf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hro5fmf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ijxrrqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ijxrrqh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陈独秀：青春如初春，如朝日，如百卉之萌动，如利刃之新发于硎(xíng)，人生最宝贵之时期也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-883knnc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-883knnc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p69jtv3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p69jtv3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舒婷《致橡树》：我们分担寒潮、风雷、霹雳；我们共享雾霭流岚、虹霓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d0fo7rx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d0fo7rx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0ensbvg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0ensbvg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《美丽心灵》约翰·纳什"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-87z1y82","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-87z1y82","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f8ttpby","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f8ttpby","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西格里夫·萨松：心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1zxzoxu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1zxzoxu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-59bvs4h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-59bvs4h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：大胆的见解就好比下棋时移动一个棋子，它可能被吃掉，但它却是胜局的起点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rnhfh18","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rnhfh18","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rfb2tt8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rfb2tt8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：西西弗斯无声的全部快乐就在于：他的命运是属于他的，他的岩石是他的事情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xkntgj5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xkntgj5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qluzw37","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qluzw37","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：在隆冬，我终于知道，我身上有一个不可战胜的夏天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4hjh84f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4hjh84f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-n8coljb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n8coljb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：一个人可以被毁灭， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"mark","TextMarkTextContent":"但不能被打败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kzbz5dn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kzbz5dn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-62vf2ko","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-62vf2ko","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杨绛：生活一半是柴米油盐，一半是星辰大海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6terujh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6terujh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-24rpnhp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-24rpnhp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰：世界上只有一种英雄主义，就是在认清生活的真相之后依然热爱生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5pkrutd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5pkrutd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qw9krno","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qw9krno","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗素：参差多态乃是人类幸福的本源。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m8hiq1i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m8hiq1i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p1249op","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p1249op","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昭昭若日月之明，离离如星辰之行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gggfukq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gggfukq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nvwyymb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nvwyymb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"事以急败，思因缓得。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sxoufe1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sxoufe1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1csu8fi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1csu8fi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"晚来风定钓丝闲，上下是新月。千里水天一色，看孤鸿明灭。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-95imifn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-95imifn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ysui4de","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ysui4de","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍《骆驼祥子》：经验是生活的肥料，有什么样的经验便变成什么样的人，在沙漠里养不出牡丹来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-831jucz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-831jucz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hy5l1op","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hy5l1op","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黄金累千，不如一贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8ipaf0e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8ipaf0e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9bcpkpx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9bcpkpx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：理论是灰色的，唯生命之树常青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1zxje4u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1zxje4u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j6z1k4f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j6z1k4f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道不同，不相为谋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ieqlbvr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ieqlbvr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-41l5iw1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-41l5iw1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浴不必江海，要之去垢；马不必骐骥，要之善走。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7ym66xy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ym66xy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wtc4x2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wtc4x2a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟利于民不必法古，苟周于事不必循旧。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yfr2vqb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yfr2vqb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-68qrg9o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-68qrg9o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怀重宝者，不以夜行；任大功者，不以轻敌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-udhedlw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-udhedlw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-81ezjbu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-81ezjbu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独行穿落叶，闲坐数流萤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iz4amcx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iz4amcx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3rcz3nc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3rcz3nc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"佯北勿从，锐卒勿攻，饵兵勿食。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dzofolg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dzofolg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f0wvd05","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f0wvd05","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：只有流过血的手指，才能弹出世间的绝唱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-h2uvbo4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h2uvbo4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fgzzrsj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fgzzrsj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特鲁多医生墓志铭：医生有时治愈，常常帮助，总是安慰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gntzbqz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gntzbqz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qbpi95b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qbpi95b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《蛤蟆先生去看心理医生》：没有一种批判比自我批判更强烈，也没有一个法官比我们自己更严苛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d5p5r54","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d5p5r54","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p2bsgcr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p2bsgcr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"德不孤，必有邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5lt1m3p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5lt1m3p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fclg0e8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fclg0e8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吹灭读书灯，一身都是月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rdd0yb8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rdd0yb8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-04uqko1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-04uqko1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：“昨夜西风凋碧树，独上高楼，望尽天涯路”，此第一境也；“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”，此第二境也；“众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处”，此第三境也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kniahdv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kniahdv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fzbr4wx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fzbr4wx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勿以身贵而贱人，勿以独见而违众。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z2pqlnn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z2pqlnn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-455zpae","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-455zpae","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山河虽无恙，吾辈当自强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-q8a425x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q8a425x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kudt400","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kudt400","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君埋泉下泥销骨，我寄人间雪满头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ibumynj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ibumynj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-704n8a2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-704n8a2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蛇蛇硕言，出自口矣。巧言如簧，颜之厚矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dmvhl7o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dmvhl7o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-oqxu5yx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oqxu5yx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良剑期乎断，不期乎镆铘；良马期乎千里，不期乎骥骜(jì ào)。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gwp0k4z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gwp0k4z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ji4bcz7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ji4bcz7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勤能补拙，学可医愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v55ozk0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v55ozk0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wmzwecs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wmzwecs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州。请君暂上凌烟阁，若个书生万户侯？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vd8tnlt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vd8tnlt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s3dsnm0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s3dsnm0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为政不难，不得罪于巨室。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-evmmqbh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-evmmqbh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sdc9m34","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sdc9m34","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长恨人心不如水，等闲平地起波澜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9xiallu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9xiallu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gms7z3m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gms7z3m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"试玉要烧三日满，辨材须待七年期。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pei9al9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pei9al9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lpfv10q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lpfv10q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"清风一枕南窗卧，闲阅床头几卷书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nq65ztu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nq65ztu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7e86h6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7e86h6j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不知而自以为知，百祸之宗也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1c76i5l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1c76i5l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-n4lc7c9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n4lc7c9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"轻财足以聚人，律己足以服人，量宽足以得人，身先足以率人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-06yz61t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-06yz61t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fz6o9vg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fz6o9vg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，不如一忍。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qjp2m9d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qjp2m9d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2iawyef","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2iawyef","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功名半纸，风雪千山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zwfxnqu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zwfxnqu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ir5ioux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ir5ioux","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"井以甘竭，李以苦成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-48idfle","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-48idfle","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-clqrsse","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-clqrsse","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠君明月满前溪，直到西湖畔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vp6kwab","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vp6kwab","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rfos610","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rfos610","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道虽迩(ěr)，不行不至；事虽小，不为不成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-a3ysw8m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a3ysw8m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i7uajl7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i7uajl7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为草当作兰，为木当作松。兰秋香风远，松寒不改容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-58awjts","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-58awjts","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fwim05j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fwim05j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用威者不轻怒，善用恩者不妄施。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s3h3oz0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s3h3oz0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s5d2ura","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s5d2ura","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马先驯而后求良，人先信而后求能。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wpba9jx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wpba9jx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s2st2jb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s2st2jb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d2xri8u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d2xri8u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d9093pt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d9093pt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人要是不能从过程中体味幸福和快乐，生命就成了一场荒诞的苦役。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-klc46j1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-klc46j1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rc7yjze","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rc7yjze","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君王城上竖降旗，妾在深宫那得知？十四万人齐解甲，更无一个是男儿！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jh6abrn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jh6abrn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1y86puh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1y86puh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，避其锐气，击其惰归，此治气者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1zakmbt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1zakmbt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cjk7rdz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cjk7rdz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政入万山围子里，一山放出一山拦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-erhqof4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-erhqof4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m1gztva","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m1gztva","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地者万物之逆旅也；光阴者百代之过客也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wbdhn3f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wbdhn3f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f2esrjd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f2esrjd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽不能至，心向往之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hkcpy3x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hkcpy3x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1fhx762","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1fhx762","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高者未必贤，下者未必愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fzbu0hh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fzbu0hh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yk1py6m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yk1py6m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与朋友交游，须将他们好处留心学来，方能受益；对圣贤言语，必要我平时照样行去，才算读书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vqv48nj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vqv48nj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1v7arhj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1v7arhj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二人同心，其利断金；同心之言，其臭(xiù)如兰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-esi0gu7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-esi0gu7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jkcgjwz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jkcgjwz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子不蔽人之美，不言人之恶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cg6pnhr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cg6pnhr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ozobhyb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ozobhyb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-peqtgvz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-peqtgvz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5n6t5f1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5n6t5f1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道德用于自律时好过一切法律，用于律他时坏过一切私刑！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-o5qkdtw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o5qkdtw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kdkno1l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kdkno1l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山高自有客行路，水深自有渡船人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-245cuau","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-245cuau","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fedyugb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fedyugb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e5wg9zv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e5wg9zv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jdsv0c6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jdsv0c6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不忘初心，方得始终。初心易得，始终难守。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uzx8gof","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uzx8gof","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kfdsymi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kfdsymi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不迁怒，不贰过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tx8o8ft","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tx8o8ft","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g89np1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g89np1f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用兵之法，十则围之，五则攻之，倍则分之，敌则能战之，少则能逃之，不若则能避之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ah4ygdd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ah4ygdd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xfstjcp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xfstjcp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"越自尊大，越见器小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z7q2do0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z7q2do0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9ujz9vy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9ujz9vy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浮云一别后，流水十年间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c2o8haj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c2o8haj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bqxenpy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bqxenpy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穆勒 ：个人的自由，以不侵犯他人的自由为自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-np3310b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-np3310b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-54r4xtw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-54r4xtw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小舟从此逝，江海寄余生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p5lvvj7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p5lvvj7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5wnyojo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5wnyojo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云山苍苍，江水泱泱，先生之风，山高水长！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ujwwf23","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ujwwf23","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yibxy9o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yibxy9o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"行远道者假于车，济江海者因于舟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-97gbzrl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-97gbzrl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a72jart","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a72jart","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p92cgwy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p92cgwy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4xe4txv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4xe4txv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立志欲坚不欲锐，成功在久不在速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-egl9wer","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-egl9wer","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m7k6khv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m7k6khv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zivveg7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zivveg7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nuqe9p5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nuqe9p5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布伦南：手头上有点钱的人认为爱是世界上最重要的东西，而穷人则明白世界上最重要的是金钱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l7pn2lk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l7pn2lk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o4h6jqm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o4h6jqm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"冯至《十四行集》：我们准备着，深深地领受，那些意想不到的奇迹。在漫长的岁月里，忽然有彗星的出现，狂风乍起。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kdbco6v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kdbco6v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ft5fcj1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ft5fcj1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"疾风怒雨，禽鸟戚戚；霁月光风，草木欣欣。天地不可一日无和气，人心不可一日无喜神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yfr7jb3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yfr7jb3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jpgckhp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jpgckhp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫之高华，只在于道德气节。鄙夫之炫耀，但求诸服饰起居。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uqixlck","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uqixlck","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tts7w7j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tts7w7j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"甘井近竭，招木近伐。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8x36l2j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8x36l2j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dkkeby1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dkkeby1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，屈人之兵而非战也，拔人之城而非攻也，毁人之国而非久也，必以全争于天下。故兵不顿而利可全，此谋攻之法也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p7xxpj8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p7xxpj8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3zmzjqc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3zmzjqc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你吞并一切，像远方，像大海，像时间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qmxkhu5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qmxkhu5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p51hqfa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p51hqfa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"挟取笔端风雨，快写胸中丘壑，不肯下樊笼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-i6q6g7x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i6q6g7x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-n78501g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n78501g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴尔扎克：一星陨落，黯淡不了星空灿烂；一花凋零，荒芜不了整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m1dmxgk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m1dmxgk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fmiu9th","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fmiu9th","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"伯修斯：在所有不幸中，最不幸的事是曾经幸福过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zkf95r7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zkf95r7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3ez3o1w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3ez3o1w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草萤有耀终非火，荷露虽团岂是珠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mdagqj7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mdagqj7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7udooie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7udooie","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"耳闻之不如目见之，目见之不如足践之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-138rcha","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-138rcha","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5luvp5q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5luvp5q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卖花担上，买得一枝春欲放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-291qb0z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-291qb0z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w8wb7l9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w8wb7l9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亭亭山上松，瑟(sè)瑟谷中风。风声一何盛，松枝一何劲。冰霜正惨凄，终岁常端正。岂不罹(lí)凝寒，松柏有本性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nqrsqhf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nqrsqhf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sdptrgj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sdptrgj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好问则裕，自用则小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-r2uhqex","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r2uhqex","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i67p4a9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i67p4a9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雾失楼台，月迷津渡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vjgai6h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vjgai6h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wp6157x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wp6157x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：世界以痛吻我，我也要报之以歌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-offl96a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-offl96a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pf8puri","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pf8puri","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人之诺诺，不如一士之谔谔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d1p0hgf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d1p0hgf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h86ils8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h86ils8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早岁读书无甚解，晚年省事有奇功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1hdemec","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1hdemec","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-juv5n34","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-juv5n34","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你所浪费的今天，是昨天死去的人奢望的明天；你所厌恶的现在，是未来的你回不去的曾经。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5hwt4tv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5hwt4tv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xbj2sme","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xbj2sme","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：有很多人常常抱怨没有机会，其实没有机会本身亦是一个机会：一个锻炼自己耐力和充分积蓄自己力量的机会。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iesvwtp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iesvwtp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u5mo7v5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u5mo7v5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世界让我遍体鳞伤，但伤口长出的却是翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ld2rwsa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ld2rwsa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l9h9142","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l9h9142","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡战者，以正合，以奇胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-71ruvxn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-71ruvxn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7j3gpmu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7j3gpmu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方其中，圆其外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e6yeut8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e6yeut8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6bhxq35","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6bhxq35","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独学而无友，则孤陋而寡闻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gvbmjsk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gvbmjsk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w4bh3h2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w4bh3h2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：苦难既然把我推到了悬崖的边缘，那么就让我在这悬崖的边缘坐下来，顺便看看悬崖下的流岚雾霭，唱支歌给你听。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ykb3z20","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ykb3z20","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ia3dy68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ia3dy68","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国虽大，好战必亡；天下虽安，忘战必危。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hu1bunz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hu1bunz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o4jp5ny","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o4jp5ny","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：每个冬天的句号都是春暖花开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rayte1k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rayte1k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ba1e682","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ba1e682","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百里趋利，兵家所忌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mt4rcjf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mt4rcjf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jiwfqeu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jiwfqeu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李大钊：谁对时间越吝啬，时间对谁越慷慨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8q5fhyx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8q5fhyx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dce8yrh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dce8yrh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粗缯大布裹生涯，腹有诗书气自华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mcudgdq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mcudgdq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ujtgt5v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ujtgt5v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7igakdo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7igakdo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tw7rpap","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tw7rpap","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"慈不掌兵，情不立事，义不理财，善不为官。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2vieoo3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2vieoo3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-r5uvtej","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r5uvtej","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大巧在所不为，大智在所不虑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p7mqq60","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p7mqq60","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a2kxdzq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a2kxdzq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海到尽头天作岸，山登绝顶我为峰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-eoec5le","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-eoec5le","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-trr905h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-trr905h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨之为物，能令昼短，能令夜长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-o3x7tmd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o3x7tmd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s69lrcv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s69lrcv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善出奇者，无穷如天地，不竭如江海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-o0vmwuh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o0vmwuh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gkkp84p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gkkp84p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫行事，当磊磊落落，如日月皎然。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y7qrao5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y7qrao5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7obkb30","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7obkb30","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者行之始，行者知之成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8j3e050","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8j3e050","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5r1hxj1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5r1hxj1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者不以短击长，而以长击短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-13g1g1i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-13g1g1i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0uw6417","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0uw6417","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"振衣千仞冈，濯足万里流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kn3osux","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kn3osux","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-itz5ixs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-itz5ixs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：你今天受的苦、吃的亏、担的责、扛的罪、忍的痛，到最后都会变成光，照亮你的路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y7f0tfg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y7f0tfg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-t2estvl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t2estvl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张而不弛，文武弗能也；弛而不张，文武弗为也。一张一弛，文武之道也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-veavgz7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-veavgz7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hunbjw7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hunbjw7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善为士者，不武；善战者，不怒；善胜敌者，不与；善用人者，为之下。是谓不争之德，是谓用人之力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-onuhr4e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-onuhr4e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-823k90t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-823k90t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中心藏之，何日忘之！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-01n8v4s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-01n8v4s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tlqiipm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tlqiipm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：没有比脚更长的路，没有比人更高的山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p5aw1e6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p5aw1e6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-93v9weu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-93v9weu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：才能是在寂静中造就，而品格则是在世间汹涌波涛中形成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ui77nm0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ui77nm0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pnkeb7t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pnkeb7t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有迷魂招不得，雄鸡一声天下白。少年心事当拏云，谁念幽寒坐呜呃。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uiodiwo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uiodiwo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dz74m5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dz74m5c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尺之木必有节目，寸之玉必有瑕疵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ozv04ln","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ozv04ln","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-80795y0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-80795y0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曾国藩：天下古今之庸人，皆以一惰字致败；天下古今之才人，皆以一傲字致败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ip0graa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ip0graa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l600db9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l600db9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"培根：当你孤独寂寞时，阅读可以消遣。当你高谈阔论时，知识可供装饰。当你处世行事时，正确运用知识意味着力量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yzw3o86","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yzw3o86","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wnrx5af","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wnrx5af","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"辅车相依，唇亡齿寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7yyhaw9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7yyhaw9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-93cctti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-93cctti","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"池田大作：荣誉有如萤虫之火，在黑暗的夜空里，它放着光，显示出美丽，极其可贵。但是靠近一看，立刻就会明白它是何等的软弱无力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jiksa6h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jiksa6h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-90edcog","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-90edcog","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：谁终将声震人间，必长久深自缄默；谁终将点燃闪电，必长久如云漂泊。我的时代还没有到来，有的人死后方生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w68xapw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w68xapw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dfm98tk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dfm98tk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"三毛：梦想，可以天花乱坠；理想，是我们一步一个脚印踩出来的坎坷道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j2m22rc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j2m22rc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s650942","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s650942","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志不可一日坠，心不可一日放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1ph1b63","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1ph1b63","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3dkh1zf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3dkh1zf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一双冷眼看世人，满腔热血酬知己。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1zcz9su","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1zcz9su","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hofuiyv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hofuiyv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗翔：误解是人生常态，理解是稀缺的例外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-143xlxm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-143xlxm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-771gd1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-771gd1f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杀人亦有限，列国自有疆。苟能制侵陵，岂在多杀伤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-daqjbfb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-daqjbfb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h4jztk6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h4jztk6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝闻道，夕死可矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jurlzcx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jurlzcx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cpvyoy4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cpvyoy4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫四方志，安可辞固穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ovrqw3l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ovrqw3l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s8ap0ml","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s8ap0ml","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粪虫至秽变为蝉，而饮露于秋风；腐草无光化为荧，而耀采于夏月。故知洁常自污出，明每从暗生也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-aw3jm7a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aw3jm7a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l8d6tey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l8d6tey","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"物以稀为贵，情因老更慈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bm0v71x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bm0v71x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-k8wxe5v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k8wxe5v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xl3n2d2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xl3n2d2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6itlstt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6itlstt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能受谏，安能谏人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l15oa41","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l15oa41","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4zmfyc0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4zmfyc0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生岂草木，寒暑移此心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-liulguq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-liulguq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s20f9e4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s20f9e4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫当容人，勿为人所容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-953n1n9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-953n1n9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-idfrecs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-idfrecs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不为无益之事，何以悦有涯之生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oubyz4b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oubyz4b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bdkcj5v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bdkcj5v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海棠未雨，梨花先雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-90ksq3g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-90ksq3g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qdcg7g7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qdcg7g7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地薄者大木不产，水浅者大鱼不游。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v3geugx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v3geugx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d6ijzkl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d6ijzkl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"忧勤是美德，太苦则无以适性怡情；淡泊是高风，太枯则无以济人利物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jy9y2t9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jy9y2t9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8yegrm3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8yegrm3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书为身上之用，而人以为纸上之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iuoft2f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iuoft2f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-n56h152","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n56h152","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天可补，海可填，南山可移。日月既往，不可复追。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6hqaszv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6hqaszv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lfzopla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lfzopla","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼布尔：请赐予我平静，去接受我无法改变的；给予我勇气，去改变我能改变的；赐我智慧，分辨这两者的区别。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-przd65p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-przd65p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xgrfif0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xgrfif0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"腹中贮书一万卷，不肯低头在草莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qqxcvm2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qqxcvm2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rrzon2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rrzon2g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"须知少日拏云志，曾许人间第一流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cy20iuk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cy20iuk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zjo1xb3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zjo1xb3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间的步伐有三种：未来姗姗来迟，现在像箭一样飞逝，过去永远静立不动。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w14wa4s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w14wa4s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6hrrxq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6hrrxq5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天若无雪霜，青松不如草。地若无山川，何人重平道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-in9ikby","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-in9ikby","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nraksj1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nraksj1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡心所向，素履所往，生如逆旅，一苇以航。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xw0w7jq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xw0w7jq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9zc8s34","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9zc8s34","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓事宜急干，敏则有功；急事宜缓办，忙则多错。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-flqoi8s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-flqoi8s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mxc16s2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mxc16s2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众口铄金，积毁销骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s0nruuc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s0nruuc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ad2swqo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ad2swqo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春日迟迟，卉木萋萋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7gbldkw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7gbldkw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-aiildkg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aiildkg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若有恒何必三更眠五更起，最无益莫过一日曝十日寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qp0p03s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qp0p03s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p5s0nhr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p5s0nhr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m3spnjr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m3spnjr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1v6z1jq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1v6z1jq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人之相知，贵相知心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x8hz5zt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x8hz5zt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-eeudhrs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-eeudhrs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桃李春风一杯酒，江湖夜雨十年灯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-li9c4c9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-li9c4c9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gjvmw1t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gjvmw1t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"东风知我欲山行，吹断檐间积雨声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gj9jw72","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gj9jw72","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u4njx07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u4njx07","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桐花万里丹山路，雏凤清于老凤声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3d4cvv7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3d4cvv7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vwhqi30","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vwhqi30","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不能设计，你只能面对。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z8vccef","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z8vccef","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wc2a5l5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wc2a5l5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地不仁，以万物为刍狗；圣人不仁，以百姓为刍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fc65i83","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fc65i83","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-35il0af","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-35il0af","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心随长风去，吹散万里云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vmpk1vw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vmpk1vw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s1yq3x9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s1yq3x9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见面怜清瘦，呼儿问苦辛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dvv0k1u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dvv0k1u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kkgh4y6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kkgh4y6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查尔斯·A·比尔德：当天空黑暗到一定程度，星辰就会熠熠生辉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kt36p5o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kt36p5o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5lw6b9v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5lw6b9v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中何以赠君别，惟有青青松树枝。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6dumxz8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6dumxz8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kul6qhg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kul6qhg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏必加于有功，刑必断于有罪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hlnfezb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hlnfezb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i9ro7l8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i9ro7l8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规小节者不能成荣名，恶小耻者不能立大功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4r06jy4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4r06jy4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-58fe5sf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-58fe5sf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"沈从文：聪明人要理解生活，愚蠢人要习惯生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-njyvjq5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-njyvjq5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cgf7zyg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cgf7zyg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"康德：世界上有两件东西能震撼人们的心灵：一件是我们心中崇高的道德标准；另一件是我们头顶上灿烂的星空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dw789mk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dw789mk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kixoevy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kixoevy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叔本华：财富就像海水，饮得越多，渴得越厉害。名望实际上也是如此。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ycutz5x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ycutz5x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wqau51j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wqau51j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵者，国之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fbswmx1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fbswmx1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-epog0lp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-epog0lp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵无常势，水无常形，能因敌变化而取胜者，谓之神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7u0q74j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7u0q74j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-07btjmv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-07btjmv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何物动人二月杏花八月桂，有谁催我三更灯火五更鸡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vuxgb2m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vuxgb2m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hn7xd7b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hn7xd7b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自古骄兵多致败，从来轻敌少成功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4mrj9r7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4mrj9r7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jp4zg9y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jp4zg9y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知往日所往之非，则学日进矣；见世人可取者多，则德日进矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6s4ka78","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6s4ka78","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3vnwnze","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3vnwnze","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马太福音：凡有的，还要加倍给他，叫他有余；没有的，连他剩余的也要夺过来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-192slld","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-192slld","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pbrynn5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pbrynn5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风流不在谈锋胜，袖手无言味最长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cpgskjg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cpgskjg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j9s0pgt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j9s0pgt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恻隐之心，人皆有之；羞恶之心，人皆有之；恭敬之心，人皆有之；是非之心，人皆有之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qumiltg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qumiltg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kmj4n6r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kmj4n6r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sm6r6ek","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sm6r6ek","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-28pi3s7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-28pi3s7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"已识乾坤大，犹怜草木青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4k3xud4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4k3xud4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-k6qerya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k6qerya","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鹏北海，凤朝阳。又携书剑路茫茫。明年此日青云上，却笑人间举子忙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0yumvy5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0yumvy5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2lt9syl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2lt9syl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝饮木兰之坠露兮，夕餐秋菊之落英。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7z8zsp0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7z8zsp0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vsnad8d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vsnad8d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人同心则得千人之力，万人异心则无一人之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ntz8336","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ntz8336","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nntwhta","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nntwhta","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出其所不趋，趋其所不意。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-q045wdq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q045wdq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qzgcg9u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qzgcg9u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"戒骄风清月朗，除躁海阔天空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hryq0ji","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hryq0ji","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0nb1s4x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0nb1s4x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何时杖尔看南雪，我与梅花两白头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gym8s6j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gym8s6j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7n1gpkc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7n1gpkc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一时宠利有尽，千秋青史难欺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7j76fjo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7j76fjo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8noby9o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8noby9o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山川异域，风月同天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-esx683g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-esx683g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8qyhf3b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8qyhf3b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白石似玉，奸佞似贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xf7f3hz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xf7f3hz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9mv4t2r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9mv4t2r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深厚的教养所集成的勇猛，远远胜过无知无情者的鲁莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mmhsx1t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mmhsx1t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jv8imay","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jv8imay","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"积财千万，不如薄技在身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-glhl4ap","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-glhl4ap","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vy2dlrg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vy2dlrg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：生活总是让我们遍体鳞伤，但到后来，那些受伤的地方一定会变成我们最强壮的地方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kwsi44b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kwsi44b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lmmqt4d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lmmqt4d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当年不肯嫁春风，无端却被秋风误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vsc05x1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vsc05x1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-74yva0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-74yva0n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良辰美景奈何天，赏心乐事谁家院。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qgsh6ey","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qgsh6ey","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hnnh360","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hnnh360","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"唤起一天明月，照我满怀冰雪，浩荡百川流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j1jztn6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j1jztn6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4u98dom","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4u98dom","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"休对故人思故国，且将新火试新茶。诗酒趁年华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-20a6fqy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-20a6fqy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hadvmwr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hadvmwr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：那些听不见音乐的人，认为那些跳舞的人疯了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pngv2fc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pngv2fc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lbaspq8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lbaspq8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：其实人跟树是一样的，越是向往高处的阳光，它的根就越要伸向黑暗的地底。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-akr33mk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-akr33mk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i9bivsz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i9bivsz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉可碎而不可改其白，竹可焚而不可毁其节。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tmddf3s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tmddf3s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2nad3ly","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2nad3ly","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"南风吹其心，摇摇为谁吐？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-13pq4a7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-13pq4a7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ooh7cx0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ooh7cx0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴金：希望是人生之需要。人如没有希望，何异江河干涸了流水？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vnwafpq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vnwafpq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5jndgbh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5jndgbh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷不失义，达不离道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d2db58l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d2db58l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tvv8nhy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tvv8nhy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为者常成，行者常至。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e75170k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e75170k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1tkl39p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1tkl39p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"青云当自致，何必求知音？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6z1qu0h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6z1qu0h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lanaadt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lanaadt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"争名者于朝，争利者于市。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fjhs4kk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fjhs4kk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tus26ox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tus26ox","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天上浮云如白衣，斯须变幻如苍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zvo8eca","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zvo8eca","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j37po6m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j37po6m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莺花犹怕春光老，岂可教人枉度春？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oat6wek","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oat6wek","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-agqw6qc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-agqw6qc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生芳秽有千载，世上荣枯无百年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k2499ba","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k2499ba","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-roh6uir","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-roh6uir","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你的欢乐和悲哀变大的时候，世界就变小了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k6o7ci2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k6o7ci2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ue5aa1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ue5aa1c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故将有五危，必死可杀，必生可虏，忿速可侮，廉洁可辱，爱民可烦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jztz26q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jztz26q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ws80pkf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ws80pkf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纵使文章惊海内，纸上苍生而已。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hs12v7v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hs12v7v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-laeo55h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-laeo55h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死生契阔，与子成说。执子之手，与子偕老。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-axxbybf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-axxbybf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u35h3p8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u35h3p8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兼听则明，偏信则暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gekhrzn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gekhrzn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-eg4tpii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-eg4tpii","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"弃燕雀小志，作鸿鹄高翔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ekmhkee","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ekmhkee","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-t2e297t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t2e297t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"眼界要阔，遍历名山大川；度量要宏，熟读五经诸史。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3y1a5tn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3y1a5tn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bcg2oki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bcg2oki","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地存肝胆，江山阅鬓华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5drwcmg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5drwcmg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bfcrv43","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bfcrv43","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不相见，动如参与商。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-63nomj1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-63nomj1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uc2e08m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uc2e08m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莫道君行早，更有早行人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pxcuas5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pxcuas5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3c3mdal","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3c3mdal","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大人者，不失其赤子之心者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lgp6mtr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lgp6mtr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-12h6i9p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-12h6i9p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"英雄者，胸怀大志，腹有良谋，有包藏宇宙之机，吞吐天地之志者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-u77zcgy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u77zcgy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mxtdh8j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mxtdh8j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪里温柔，水边明秀，不借春工力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e1m6vcb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e1m6vcb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xg75zll","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xg75zll","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良言一句三冬暖，恶语伤人六月寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gn8ccex","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gn8ccex","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mfsf0og","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mfsf0og","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学如弓弩，才如箭镞。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2f5f4py","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2f5f4py","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j4ku6sn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j4ku6sn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人不读书，其犹夜行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-23kqhjd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-23kqhjd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6ta52t1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6ta52t1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷猿奔林，岂暇择木！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-asdls0k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-asdls0k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cl6jn1g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cl6jn1g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令在必信，法在必行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8ochhif","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8ochhif","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y5xnzq7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y5xnzq7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其疾如风，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不动如山，难知如阴，动如雷震。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ordze59","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ordze59","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-accodmo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-accodmo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4k8lrq4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4k8lrq4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ivlulhv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ivlulhv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我亦飘零久！十年来，深恩负尽，死生师友。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mr9sdpe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mr9sdpe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-oh6uv49","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oh6uv49","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"板凳要坐十年冷，文章不写一句空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ur1upmw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ur1upmw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s69ptjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s69ptjm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有心为善，虽善不赏；无心为恶，虽恶不罚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gdqnpk9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gdqnpk9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q111a7j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q111a7j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不目见口问，不能尽知也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0wow0dh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0wow0dh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5a6h1h5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5a6h1h5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一年之计，莫如树谷；十年之计，莫如树木；终身之计，莫如树人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uydtyg2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uydtyg2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-61hqqc9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-61hqqc9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不因幸运而故步自封，不因厄运而一蹶不振。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rrsj3px","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rrsj3px","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j2wp71t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j2wp71t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良弓难张，然可以及高入深；良马难乘，然可以任重致远。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c3a1ezc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c3a1ezc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z7hsypo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z7hsypo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上兵伐谋，其次伐交，其次伐兵，其下攻城。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5vrc62y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5vrc62y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m29hwqe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m29hwqe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志合者不以山海为远，道乖者不以咫尺为近。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1m4t0rw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1m4t0rw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-k89rpl2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k89rpl2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海水梦悠悠，君愁我亦愁。南风知我意，吹梦到西洲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qh2by1z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qh2by1z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lf7wwl1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lf7wwl1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不幸者常常愿意同幸运者相比，抱怨自己的运气。幸运者常常不愿同不幸者相比，相信自己的努力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-f1qb7nd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f1qb7nd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g733qxp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g733qxp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怯生于勇，弱生于强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dzz0265","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dzz0265","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uur3m7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uur3m7d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贵上极则反贱，贱下极则反贵。贵出如粪土，贱取如珠玉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ky4kn1u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ky4kn1u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-c1pg4p0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c1pg4p0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有志者事竟成破釜沉舟百二秦关终属楚，苦心人天不负卧薪尝胆三千越甲可吞吴。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xmir5oz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xmir5oz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yyrbjtu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yyrbjtu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔日之得不足以自衿，今日之成不容以自限。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-u5xgdb6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u5xgdb6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6ev88ji","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6ev88ji","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不善操舟者，恶河之曲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v1cak6t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v1cak6t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fmvt6ps","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fmvt6ps","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操千曲而后晓声，观千剑而后识器。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ylam66t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ylam66t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xsvv2s9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xsvv2s9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长安何处在，只在马蹄下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jsert4z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jsert4z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hxe6cce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hxe6cce","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人情阅尽秋云厚，世事经多蜀道平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5lmeuxt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5lmeuxt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jpcxpsn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jpcxpsn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志行万里者，不中道而辍足。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hhcm54u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hhcm54u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-35wbwzk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-35wbwzk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交友须带三分侠气，做人要存一点素心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zqlkppb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zqlkppb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1914obq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1914obq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿不展风云志，空负天生八尺躯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jjrufhv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jjrufhv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7yoc2hs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7yoc2hs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"愿作远方兽，步步比肩行。愿作深山木，枝枝连理生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3at7t7i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3at7t7i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wgmwp08","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wgmwp08","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵不厌诈，将贵知机。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hq7nq6e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hq7nq6e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6sk1bry","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6sk1bry","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上士闻道，勤而行之；中士闻道，若存若亡；下士闻道，大笑之。不笑不足以为道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-85q6mpc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-85q6mpc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-axsd738","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-axsd738","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子慎始，差若毫厘，缪以千里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9bbygmx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9bbygmx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gwckunp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gwckunp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古来多被虚名误，宁负虚名身莫负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-aegc86j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aegc86j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wdhw1ur","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wdhw1ur","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我志在寥阔，畴昔梦登天。摩挲素月，俯仰已千年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j2n1x7j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j2n1x7j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y6mg4b3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y6mg4b3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们每个人出生的时候，并非是两手空空，而是捏了一张生命的借记卡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pwi6xyn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pwi6xyn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4dyenv1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4dyenv1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好风凭借力，送我上青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kj2terr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kj2terr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f87xxgm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f87xxgm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉在山而草木润，渊生珠而崖不枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k4k912i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k4k912i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3g25jgd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3g25jgd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学之染人，甚于丹青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-17oy864","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-17oy864","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ukq20uh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ukq20uh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地有万古，此身不再得；人生只百年，此日最易过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-edoapbf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-edoapbf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g4eu5x2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g4eu5x2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十有九人堪白眼，百无一用是书生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wqldjgx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wqldjgx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d7x0rn5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d7x0rn5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫志四海，万里犹比邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-a1wi0mt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a1wi0mt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ox4ix3g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ox4ix3g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仗义每多屠狗辈，负心多是读书人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gr4ufg4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gr4ufg4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bbl6ncs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bbl6ncs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"涓涓不塞，将为江河。荧荧不救，炎炎奈何。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lwo03h8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lwo03h8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-80ajgzl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-80ajgzl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如寄，多忧何为？今我不乐，岁月如驰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1oqk4z0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1oqk4z0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p0lmaw1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p0lmaw1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天行有常，不为尧存，不为桀亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x7s51x8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x7s51x8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ygji2am","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ygji2am","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书志在圣贤，非徒科第；为官心存君国，岂计身家？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-73awpnj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-73awpnj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-og5j65s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-og5j65s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少而好学，如日出之阳；壮而好学，如日中之光；老而好学，如秉烛之明。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9w09wzw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9w09wzw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lmsnxwg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lmsnxwg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纪伯伦：不要因为走得太远而忘记为什么出发。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mr0g1g0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mr0g1g0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pno1r4p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pno1r4p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用赏者贵信，用罚者贵必。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v8rgh1y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v8rgh1y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-btcwl7i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-btcwl7i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"傲不可长，欲不可纵，乐不可极，志不可满。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ye4373r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ye4373r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o9zkd93","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o9zkd93","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子爱财，取之有道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4qawd2n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4qawd2n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a8cfpzn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a8cfpzn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"余光中：敢在时间里自焚的人，必在永恒里结晶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pfwatjb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pfwatjb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-t95ssn4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t95ssn4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主不可以怒而兴师，将不可以愠而致战；合于利而动，不合于利而止。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s8p6dqk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s8p6dqk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q9fbepq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q9fbepq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fsy06ko","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fsy06ko","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m29kma3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m29kma3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海子：永远是这样，风后面是风，天空上面是天空，道路前面还是道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xz6ii7a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xz6ii7a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j30d1n6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j30d1n6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：如果你抑郁了，说明你活在过去；如果你焦虑了，说明你活在未来；如果你平静了，才说明你活在现在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2c0r2dg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2c0r2dg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pqf1wo1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pqf1wo1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对愁人勿乐，对哭人勿笑，对失意人勿矜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-b79uj73","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b79uj73","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6aryqko","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6aryqko","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知胜有五：知可以战与不可以战者胜，识众寡之用者胜，上下同欲者胜，以虞待不虞者胜，将能而君不御者胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-25f7ei1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-25f7ei1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hnqmiwt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hnqmiwt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钝学累功，不妨精熟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fufctdq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fufctdq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-b608q4e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b608q4e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"闭门即是深山，读书随处净土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3aga9kw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3aga9kw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6sfn1qy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6sfn1qy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人非生而知之者，孰能无惑?惑而不从师，其为惑也，终不解矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vxxr827","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vxxr827","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y87fnga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y87fnga","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见胜不过众人之所知，非善之善者也；战胜而天下曰善，非善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-56278mk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-56278mk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dbqb00o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dbqb00o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"折芦花赠远，零落一身秋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-01n4k3s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-01n4k3s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zlzpi48","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zlzpi48","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老骥伏枥志千里，短锥处囊半寸锋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-posnt4m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-posnt4m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kt68t6i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kt68t6i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只要厄运打不垮信念，希望之光就会驱散绝望之云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cy7n268","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cy7n268","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qieymbt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qieymbt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以势交者，势尽则疏，以利合者，利尽则散。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l6q0ltk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l6q0ltk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fs75wbr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fs75wbr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如月之恒，如日之升。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m0n9r2t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m0n9r2t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tx2z69b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tx2z69b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合军聚众，务在激气。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z2qd34o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z2qd34o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-68gb5r8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-68gb5r8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贝尔纳：构成我们学习最大障碍的是已知的东西，而不是未知的东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9n7des4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9n7des4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j91kubi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j91kubi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"约瑟夫·海勒《第二十二条军规》：任何值得为它而死的东西，肯定值得为它而生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-f31wwed","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f31wwed","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tp58bth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tp58bth","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云路鹏程九万里，雪窗萤火二十年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oqfgw1d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oqfgw1d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-us7hmnc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-us7hmnc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"华而不实，怨之所聚也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tb3xzwc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tb3xzwc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tfeckb6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tfeckb6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"精卫衔微木，将以填沧海；刑天舞干戚，猛志固常在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uh2idiw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uh2idiw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-627olwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-627olwn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4ukup8s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4ukup8s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fdfl6y0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fdfl6y0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丹青不知老将至，富贵于我如浮云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-38apaea","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-38apaea","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ezmojr3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ezmojr3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"胡适：凡富于创造性的人必敏于模仿，凡不善于模仿的人决不能创造。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sw56n26","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sw56n26","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nuyhq06","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nuyhq06","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"节义傲青云，文章高白雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5os0dt8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5os0dt8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-67kief3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-67kief3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提得起，放得下，算得到，做得完，看得破，撇得开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ok6zjw5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ok6zjw5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rotjugb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rotjugb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪曾祺：一定要爱着点什么，恰似草木对光阴的钟情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8dwy3q2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8dwy3q2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i0ddaon","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i0ddaon","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有所念人，隔在远远乡。我有所感事，结在深深肠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2h72exd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2h72exd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vqi96km","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vqi96km","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草不谢荣于春风，木不怨落于秋天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ed6n2tx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ed6n2tx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d8n0hda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d8n0hda","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一竹一兰一石，有节有香有骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yqh9vcb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yqh9vcb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gkhi9so","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gkhi9so","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"笔落惊风雨，诗成泣鬼神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kpq30q7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kpq30q7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jd5m2nt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jd5m2nt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合抱之木，生于毫末；九层之台，起于累土；千里之行，始于足下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t34oiy5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t34oiy5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lcsxh29","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lcsxh29","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山不让尘，川不辞盈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k8d2d8a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k8d2d8a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-70sigte","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-70sigte","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"皑如山上雪，皎若云间月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-28msd6p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-28msd6p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yyhyopl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yyhyopl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客子光阴诗卷里，杏花消息雨声中。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lu21p95","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lu21p95","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-79vvyu0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-79vvyu0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：我们的眼睛就是我们的监狱，而目光所及之处就是监狱的围墙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6dlvl98","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6dlvl98","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1tpvfki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1tpvfki","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中送炭人间少，锦上添花世上多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8brsr49","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8brsr49","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o483lce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o483lce","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蒲柳之姿，望秋而落；松柏之质，经霜弥茂。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nh9nn11","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nh9nn11","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-my67c4j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-my67c4j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不戚戚于贫贱，不汲汲于富贵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sm3zyy8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sm3zyy8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hnu8qnn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hnu8qnn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"门前红叶地，不扫待知音。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cyu1dku","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cyu1dku","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9nj3tdc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9nj3tdc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"村上春树：这个世界上根本没有正确的选择，我们只不过是要努力奋斗，使当初的选择变得正确。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-djvx0wm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-djvx0wm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dnkrn5b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dnkrn5b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缘木求鱼，煎水作冰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wy9ym87","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wy9ym87","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wom71li","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wom71li","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟日新，日日新，又日新。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uxg4pkj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uxg4pkj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-45frp5s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-45frp5s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贫无可奈惟求俭，拙亦何妨只要勤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s0pkyyp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s0pkyyp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e2sbgf5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e2sbgf5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文章千古事，得失寸心知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-h7mb22p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h7mb22p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dahtt9l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dahtt9l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨滴能击穿石头，并不是下落的速度快，而是因为掉落在石头上的次数多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yujjmao","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yujjmao","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zmgqqd6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zmgqqd6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人有逆天之时，天无绝人之路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m0p6d25","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m0p6d25","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s7cu0ww","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s7cu0ww","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宁为宇宙闲吟客，怕作乾坤窃禄人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c52hrx9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c52hrx9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6rcvis2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6rcvis2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"受光于隙见一床，受光于窗见室央，受光于庭户见一堂，受光于天下照四方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mozzdex","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mozzdex","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-did74rn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-did74rn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马不可以服重，牛不可以追速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vle2mkz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vle2mkz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fivgbfu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fivgbfu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改过不吝，从善如流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xqgvipe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xqgvipe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yv9k1tv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yv9k1tv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚负凌云万丈才，一生襟抱未曾开。鸟啼花落人何在，竹死桐枯凤不来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tfk1m9x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tfk1m9x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kcu21vd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kcu21vd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兰生幽谷，不为莫服而不芳；舟在江海，不为莫乘而不浮；君子行义，不为莫知而止休。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rwydwjo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rwydwjo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cm02ftj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cm02ftj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一日不思量，也攒眉千度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xag0c5l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xag0c5l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ojcecx0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ojcecx0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"彊弩之极，矢不能穿鲁缟；冲风之末，力不能漂鸿毛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nzms94z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nzms94z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-oa6up4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oa6up4t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时来天地皆同力，运去英雄不自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-carvbdv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-carvbdv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l7fujwv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l7fujwv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"倒持干戈，授人以柄。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x4b9w3o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x4b9w3o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e9139gz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e9139gz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生一世，草生一春。来如风雨，去似微尘。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oistfav","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oistfav","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vd0zmbf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vd0zmbf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪莱：未来不足惧，过往不须泣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d93ro73","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d93ro73","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xcxvpl2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xcxvpl2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从善如登，从恶如崩。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7m3lc63","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7m3lc63","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pp2mf5j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pp2mf5j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春生、夏长、秋收、冬藏，天之正也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mnfpae8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mnfpae8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2v2awpz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2v2awpz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前事不忘，后事之师。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vjq5snj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vjq5snj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lthpzps","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lthpzps","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逢人不说人间事，便是人间无事人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9xbupc7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9xbupc7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2d6p83t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2d6p83t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"花开花落树之常，能上能下人中强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-olbxlg4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-olbxlg4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z90osr2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z90osr2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立品同白玉，读书到青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2emcoah","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2emcoah","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1vu1ixy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1vu1ixy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陀思妥耶夫斯基：爱具体的人，不要爱抽象的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5qod5qk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5qod5qk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gjanpbq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gjanpbq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凭君莫话封侯事，一将功成万骨枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jluuhyi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jluuhyi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dhjm175","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dhjm175","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下皆知美之为美，斯恶已。皆知善之为善，斯不善已。有无相生，难易相成，长短相形，高下相盈，音声相和，前后相随，恒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lwkzbj6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lwkzbj6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-luvleh6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-luvleh6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子之心事，天青日白，不可使人不知；君子之才华，玉韫珠藏，不可使人易知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ryknlsy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ryknlsy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-trb02ms","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-trb02ms","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除掉荒草的最好办法，不是让除完草的土地荒着，而是种上庄稼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s1e7t0g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s1e7t0g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8hynt97","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8hynt97","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善战者，求之于势，不责于人。故能择人而任势。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-13omgpz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-13omgpz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yfw49ww","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yfw49ww","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"川泽纳污，所以成其深；山岳藏疾，所以就其大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v85umfo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v85umfo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gc14zu4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gc14zu4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"覆水不可收，行云难重寻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gx0o7qs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gx0o7qs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f7ozcwg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f7ozcwg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相鼠有皮，人而无仪！人而无仪，不死何为？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-faijawl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-faijawl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sari6xe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sari6xe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yxai9az","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yxai9az","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pj78ryl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pj78ryl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"狡兔死，走狗烹；飞鸟尽，良弓藏；敌国破，谋臣亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bkhkarr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bkhkarr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ytvwsdv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ytvwsdv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马丁·路德·金：我们这一代人终将感到悔恨，不仅仅因为坏人的可憎言行，更因为好人的可怕沉默。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yie9is4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yie9is4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-eujqa3p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-eujqa3p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我本将心向明月，奈何明月照沟渠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7tx6d62","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7tx6d62","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ydhx22e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ydhx22e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网；扬汤止沸，不如去火抽薪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-so564o8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-so564o8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lgzqkhy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lgzqkhy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"芳林新叶催陈叶，流水前波让后波。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wun1y9w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wun1y9w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2bc80jy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2bc80jy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日出扶桑一丈高，人间万事细如毛。野夫怒见不平处，磨损胸中万古刀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dkosboa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dkosboa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rdz3zwb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rdz3zwb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：果实的事业是尊贵的，花的事业是甜美的，但是让我做叶的事业吧，叶是谦逊地、专心地垂着绿荫的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0diurd1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0diurd1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nj2ev1l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nj2ev1l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子耻不修，不耻见污。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-i7xroj3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i7xroj3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tt9mcgo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tt9mcgo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陶行知：做学问就是要学要问。光学不问，只做到一半；光问不学，也只是一半。又学又问，才是完整的学问。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ye9ir7a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ye9ir7a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wd962n0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wd962n0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恶不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s3wt44l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s3wt44l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pd0p0ul","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pd0p0ul","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众里嫣然通一顾，人间颜色如尘土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2mtyqib","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2mtyqib","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bt80evw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bt80evw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将者，智、信、仁、勇、严也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yllq8w7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yllq8w7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h9v9tp2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h9v9tp2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍：才华是刀刃，辛苦是磨刀石。很锋利的刀刃，若日久不用石磨，也会生锈，成为废物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ik3w4kv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ik3w4kv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-izy31jv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-izy31jv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少年侠气，交结五都雄。肝胆洞，毛发耸。立谈中，死生同。一诺千金重。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zcach75","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zcach75","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-es7h55n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-es7h55n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰 ：一个人的绝对自由是疯狂，一个国家的绝对自由是混乱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tyotzix","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tyotzix","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-oy1dx8b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oy1dx8b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学然后知不足，教然后知困。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kdd4sbb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kdd4sbb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5kxxssu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5kxxssu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记人之长，忘人之短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qwobqck","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qwobqck","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uqxdu0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uqxdu0c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知彼知己者，百战不殆；不知彼而知己，一胜一负，不知彼，不知己，每战必殆。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-i81ojam","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i81ojam","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4vk1wfd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4vk1wfd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"月缺不改光，剑折不改刚。月缺魄易满，剑折铸复良。势利压山岳，难屈志士肠。男儿自有守，可杀不可苟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s1mb6y0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s1mb6y0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-eono9gr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-eono9gr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生贵相知，何必金与钱？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iq65dfz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iq65dfz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q16q81u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q16q81u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有真才者，必不矜才。有实学者，必不夸学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1lq1tf0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1lq1tf0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sev9ak0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sev9ak0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"薄我货者也，欲与我市者也；訾我行者，欲与我友者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xf76qhn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xf76qhn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rf66ghq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rf66ghq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风乍起，吹皱一池春水。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7julm2i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7julm2i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-37564b1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-37564b1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生万事须自为，跬步江山即寥廓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pgmwp87","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pgmwp87","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1omz3ms","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1omz3ms","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十年磨一剑，霜刃未曾试。今日把示君，谁有不平事？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j0o1o55","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j0o1o55","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mzfcfax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mzfcfax","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草木秋死，松柏独在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cqh4jgq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cqh4jgq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z4j6xov","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z4j6xov","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生是一匹马，轻快而健壮的马。人，要像骑手那样大胆而细心地驾驭它。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2wtmohf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2wtmohf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u2j4qzr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u2j4qzr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"水广者鱼大，山高者树修。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lpl80fy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lpl80fy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-labm711","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-labm711","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如梦，把梦看得太认真，固然是个大傻瓜；但以为人生如梦，就以为不必认真，也是个头等大傻瓜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-giruiwa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-giruiwa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-86virhu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-86virhu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一叶浮萍归大海，为人何处不相逢！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wcbi8k0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wcbi8k0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bir6wb8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bir6wb8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"力田不如逢年，善仕不如遇合。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4sgmkxz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4sgmkxz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bowgj6r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bowgj6r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道路难行钱作马，城池不克酒为兵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vj9le3e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vj9le3e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6d63buf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6d63buf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古人云，“读书百遍，其义自见”。谓读得熟，则不待解说，自晓其义也。余尝谓，读书有三到，谓心到，眼到，口到。心不在此，则眼不看仔细，心眼既不专一，却只漫浪诵读，决不能记，记亦不能久也。三到之中，心到最急。心既到矣，眼口岂不到乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kmnc72z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kmnc72z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6ln2wsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6ln2wsb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知人者智，自知者明。胜人者有力，自胜者强。知足者富。强行者有志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3m9mcuf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3m9mcuf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d9ubkdw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d9ubkdw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"驿寄梅花，鱼传尺素。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2i5qg72","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2i5qg72","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rt5l3ax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rt5l3ax","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自然既极博大，也极残忍，战胜一切，孕育众生。蝼蚁蚍蜉，伟人巨匠，一样在它怀抱中，和光同见。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-75y3zri","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-75y3zri","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-50hbc6h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-50hbc6h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：与恶龙缠斗过久，自身亦成恶龙；凝视深渊过久，深渊将回以凝视。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-en4om5j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-en4om5j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pw846da","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pw846da","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天戴其苍，地履其黄，纵有千古，横有八荒，前途似海，来日方长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bfr5mao","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bfr5mao","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bjc4nl4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bjc4nl4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子坦荡荡，小人长戚戚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kl4eii6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kl4eii6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sno34zi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sno34zi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心中有丘壑，眉目作山河。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-otmouvu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-otmouvu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-787nkxa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-787nkxa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"寄蜉蝣于天地，渺沧海之一粟。哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-avmtlxl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-avmtlxl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sk6tb9g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sk6tb9g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明代思想家袁了凡：昨日种种，譬如昨日死；今日种种，譬如今日生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e9zpfgi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e9zpfgi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l2ggxsx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l2ggxsx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黑格尔：只有永远躺在泥坑里的人，才不会再掉进坑里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-phvnh7h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-phvnh7h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-x8sjjsg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x8sjjsg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：每一个不曾起舞的日子都是对生命的辜负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6pbpaku","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6pbpaku","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0zzhgxo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0zzhgxo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子在齐闻《韶》，三月不知肉味，曰：‘不图为乐之至于斯也。’"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gtrqsg9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gtrqsg9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a1l2k10","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a1l2k10","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：命定的局限尽可永在，不屈的挑战却不可须臾或缺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cvm6741","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cvm6741","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v7x9ny0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v7x9ny0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：当我走向你的时候，我原想收获一缕春风，你却给了我整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qfs6kvn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qfs6kvn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fee628n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fee628n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：我相信，在群星当中有一颗星星，引领我的生命，穿越不可知的黑暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pflip6s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pflip6s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-syugqiv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-syugqiv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：心晴的时候，雨也是晴；心雨的时候，晴也是雨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9len4yt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9len4yt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3nc7469","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3nc7469","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聂卫平：遇到顺势而下的时候，就一泻千里；遇到阻碍过不去的时候，就绕一下，但我的目标一直是向前走的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-izn6y1n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-izn6y1n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nrav3iq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nrav3iq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曼德拉：我没有失败过。要么赢得胜利，要么学到东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8bqv6ec","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8bqv6ec","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2or26ow","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2or26ow","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间是单程车票，我们只能向前；而记忆是随身行李，始终伴你同行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ism7p3l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ism7p3l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8th6j3o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8th6j3o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"喷泉之所以漂亮，是因为它有压力；瀑布之所以壮观，是因为它没有退路；滴水之所以能穿石，是因为它贵在坚持。一只站在树枝上的鸟，从不害怕树枝会断裂，因为它相信的不是树枝，而是它自己的翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kfgfuat","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kfgfuat","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5q1cm81","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5q1cm81","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"追风赶月莫停留，平芜尽处是春山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s3g8cj0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s3g8cj0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gc8pmj7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gc8pmj7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼《浣溪沙·游蕲水清泉寺》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-678via2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-678via2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a1ssrdn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a1ssrdn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朱敦儒《鹧鸪天·西都作》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m7dzmji","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m7dzmji","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ssjypkt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ssjypkt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杜甫《蜀相》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vqtxfe6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vqtxfe6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ru41o45","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ru41o45","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《忆秦娥》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iqyc0qq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iqyc0qq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-14j8mf5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-14j8mf5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《上李邕》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-emae9xv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-emae9xv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-91dtaxr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-91dtaxr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游《金错刀行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t87597f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t87597f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a038inp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a038inp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李煜《虞美人》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-35qqtiz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-35qqtiz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bth4tmz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bth4tmz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白居易《琵琶行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sb7bbqe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sb7bbqe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-od6sofm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-od6sofm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"礼记《大学》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c1vc98d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c1vc98d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hedipdb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hedipdb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"范仲淹《岳阳楼记》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t70hcmr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t70hcmr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-67myzd9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-67myzd9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张若虚《春江花月夜》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-g9kexjr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g9kexjr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qd5q624","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qd5q624","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《侠客行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p3ci0vk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p3ci0vk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xnmrwtr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xnmrwtr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗经《无衣》"}]}]},{"ID":"2026060309504