tMarkTextContent":"严禁直接出现"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“对立统一”、“量变质变”、“否定之否定”等哲学术语。具体操作如下："}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ssxl9n1","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ssxl9n1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w8104vm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w8104vm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5kz6bhr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5kz6bhr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"体现矛盾转化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：分析事物内部的矛盾双方（如危与机、强与弱），阐述它们在特定条件下如何相互依存并向对立面转化。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-a7dt80j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a7dt80j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2vnjhgx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2vnjhgx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"体现积累与飞跃"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：论述从微小的积累到质的突破的过程，强调厚积薄发的重要性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yfyo5n5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yfyo5n5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9he06si","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9he06si","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"体现螺旋上升"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：展现事物发展不是简单的循环，而是看似回归原点实则境界提升的曲折前进过程。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-54ugkwj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-54ugkwj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nt7e9t1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nt7e9t1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"辅助论式拓展"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：可适当穿插使用道理/引证论证、类比论证或反证法，丰富文章的论证维度。在进行深层逻辑剖析时，可灵活调用以下思维模型，以增强文章的思辨厚度："}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ae6j8bk","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ae6j8bk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kmjipt5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kmjipt5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-re8aqft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-re8aqft","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"社会与心理效应"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：破窗效应、羊群效应、习得性无助、幸存者效应。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kboatv3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kboatv3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uo5j7gf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uo5j7gf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"决策与管理智慧"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：锚定效应、手表定律、鳄鱼法则（及时止损）、氨基酸组合效应（整体与部分）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ozdoxjv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ozdoxjv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j1ni2uz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j1ni2uz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"哲学与科学原理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：熵增定律（对抗无序）、奥卡姆剃刀（化繁为简）、墨菲定律、波普尔证伪主义、贝叶斯原理（动态认知）、皮亚杰建构主义、黑格尔辩证法、实践论。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-b9lfpx1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b9lfpx1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h8sghyd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h8sghyd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用要求：严禁直接罗列名词或进行枯燥的科学解释。必须将这些原理内化为比喻或隐喻，自然地融入论证中（例如：用“熵增”比喻精神的懈怠，用“鳄鱼法则”比喻壮士断腕的决心）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gzvkveo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gzvkveo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bn6bz10","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bn6bz10","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"论据要充分且鲜活，拒绝陈词滥调（避免过度使用司马迁、李白、爱迪生等老套素材）。结合时事热点、历史文化等多维度素材。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jpflxnd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ny4=","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jpflxnd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ag7s01o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ag7s01o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"古典底蕴与化用："}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p6h1go2","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p6h1go2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gv4mf27","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gv4mf27","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uehnxvk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uehnxvk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至少自然嵌入2–3条下面提供的的典故、文章(不必引用原文，文章总结、提炼亦可)、诗词名句、电影，并保证与论证逻辑紧密相关。"}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pog0sa3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pog0sa3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g6fi85b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g6fi85b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i9g42et","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i9g42et","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《尚书》五福：寿、福、康宁、攸好德、考终命"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nd41hfd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nd41hfd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l2xpqx4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l2xpqx4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鲁迅：无穷的远方，无数的人们，都与我相关。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6u750h3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6u750h3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rbaflcq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rbaflcq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"投之亡地然后存，陷之死地然后生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-aanjpfa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aanjpfa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qhmt6f0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qhmt6f0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t8ryidz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t8ryidz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s3v2qry","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s3v2qry","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"路遥《平凡的世界》当一个人集中地凝视着自己的不幸时，他就很难想象别人的苦难。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2go2ksf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2go2ksf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uxu4a74","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uxu4a74","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小敌之坚，大敌之擒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0mz4rad","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0mz4rad","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g79da46","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g79da46","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小人肥口，君子肥身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oy8wgj3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oy8wgj3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-knmef2c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-knmef2c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我生本无乡，心安是归处。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fktmu2m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fktmu2m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y72rn2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y72rn2p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陈独秀：青春如初春，如朝日，如百卉之萌动，如利刃之新发于硎(xíng)，人生最宝贵之时期也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ydytl3g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ydytl3g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-r4t0859","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r4t0859","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舒婷《致橡树》：我们分担寒潮、风雷、霹雳；我们共享雾霭流岚、虹霓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qzjk6k2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qzjk6k2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1l0vyrh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1l0vyrh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《美丽心灵》约翰·纳什"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xwq5o1a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xwq5o1a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8nh25jz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8nh25jz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西格里夫·萨松：心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ada5i0f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ada5i0f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1gupd6l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1gupd6l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：大胆的见解就好比下棋时移动一个棋子，它可能被吃掉，但它却是胜局的起点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s2uy23i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s2uy23i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gjzu8ay","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gjzu8ay","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：西西弗斯无声的全部快乐就在于：他的命运是属于他的，他的岩石是他的事情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0onzltj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0onzltj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z8om8k7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z8om8k7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：在隆冬，我终于知道，我身上有一个不可战胜的夏天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sx962m0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sx962m0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0q1tmxg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0q1tmxg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：一个人可以被毁灭， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"mark","TextMarkTextContent":"但不能被打败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-74lawm4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-74lawm4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6nh84ge","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6nh84ge","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杨绛：生活一半是柴米油盐，一半是星辰大海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1r6bww6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1r6bww6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e91c0uj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e91c0uj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰：世界上只有一种英雄主义，就是在认清生活的真相之后依然热爱生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s937nb1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s937nb1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y9bemv1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y9bemv1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗素：参差多态乃是人类幸福的本源。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cvu04ub","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cvu04ub","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jpgbbj1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jpgbbj1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昭昭若日月之明，离离如星辰之行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xre7ue5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xre7ue5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mrnnqd4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mrnnqd4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"事以急败，思因缓得。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-um5umgn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-um5umgn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o2hysj4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o2hysj4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"晚来风定钓丝闲，上下是新月。千里水天一色，看孤鸿明灭。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8ccz7lr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8ccz7lr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2fgj3jw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2fgj3jw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍《骆驼祥子》：经验是生活的肥料，有什么样的经验便变成什么样的人，在沙漠里养不出牡丹来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kcqgsy4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kcqgsy4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mst1bly","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mst1bly","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黄金累千，不如一贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8vngswa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8vngswa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a8gzxqu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a8gzxqu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：理论是灰色的，唯生命之树常青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7aborvr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7aborvr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1kvwqlx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1kvwqlx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道不同，不相为谋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xu2pkrp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xu2pkrp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-r16jqtg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r16jqtg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浴不必江海，要之去垢；马不必骐骥，要之善走。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wl543m1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wl543m1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kdkag1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kdkag1f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟利于民不必法古，苟周于事不必循旧。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2vfykiu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2vfykiu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jgbqutw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jgbqutw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怀重宝者，不以夜行；任大功者，不以轻敌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3wwdrwf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3wwdrwf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-t55w4xb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t55w4xb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独行穿落叶，闲坐数流萤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1s01qor","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1s01qor","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8cvq1s3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8cvq1s3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"佯北勿从，锐卒勿攻，饵兵勿食。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mvjfcef","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mvjfcef","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2hf934q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2hf934q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：只有流过血的手指，才能弹出世间的绝唱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ndojd1h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ndojd1h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jsj3pqn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jsj3pqn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特鲁多医生墓志铭：医生有时治愈，常常帮助，总是安慰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dzzuvye","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dzzuvye","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zx1orsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zx1orsb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《蛤蟆先生去看心理医生》：没有一种批判比自我批判更强烈，也没有一个法官比我们自己更严苛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x0qqdlg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x0qqdlg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d85gz23","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d85gz23","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"德不孤，必有邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5wzf1cl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5wzf1cl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l7u0x70","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l7u0x70","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吹灭读书灯，一身都是月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zwnkb8e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zwnkb8e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-inywywb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-inywywb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：“昨夜西风凋碧树，独上高楼，望尽天涯路”，此第一境也；“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”，此第二境也；“众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处”，此第三境也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e6y19vr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e6y19vr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5kv27ux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5kv27ux","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勿以身贵而贱人，勿以独见而违众。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uyjnrr0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uyjnrr0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7ebokd7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ebokd7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山河虽无恙，吾辈当自强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9c78axk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9c78axk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wtletgz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wtletgz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君埋泉下泥销骨，我寄人间雪满头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nb5gv2w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nb5gv2w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-t5ijchm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t5ijchm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蛇蛇硕言，出自口矣。巧言如簧，颜之厚矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-r5bysjz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r5bysjz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-c56roib","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c56roib","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良剑期乎断，不期乎镆铘；良马期乎千里，不期乎骥骜(jì ào)。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1h5x36t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1h5x36t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-576h7rs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-576h7rs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勤能补拙，学可医愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tvfaa1e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tvfaa1e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qyuqoak","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qyuqoak","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州。请君暂上凌烟阁，若个书生万户侯？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-g23gt8c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g23gt8c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v6xgm5o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v6xgm5o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为政不难，不得罪于巨室。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j7f2gyi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j7f2gyi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f0vx24t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f0vx24t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长恨人心不如水，等闲平地起波澜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j675smh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j675smh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bzpdsww","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bzpdsww","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"试玉要烧三日满，辨材须待七年期。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fzfkr6i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fzfkr6i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f02byln","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f02byln","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"清风一枕南窗卧，闲阅床头几卷书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hijaf57","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hijaf57","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hsdgtiz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hsdgtiz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨果：人，有了物质才能生存；有了精神，那才是生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1vgkfr1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1vgkfr1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pe04ir6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pe04ir6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨果：世界上最宽阔的是海洋，比海洋宽阔的是天空，比天空宽阔的是人的胸怀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-du8exhr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-du8exhr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8wh9pcn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8wh9pcn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨果：在逆境中，把俯视墓穴的悲痛，转换为仰望星空的情感。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-f92zr5k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f92zr5k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0slls55","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0slls55","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨果：世界上最宽阔的是海洋，比海洋宽阔的是天空，比天空宽阔的是人的胸怀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l53nevr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l53nevr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-993dmj9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-993dmj9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨果：人，有了物质才能生存；有了精神，那才是生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-58hy5yr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-58hy5yr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q53mlo0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q53mlo0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不知而自以为知，百祸之宗也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-22qyest","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-22qyest","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u435t8b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u435t8b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"轻财足以聚人，律己足以服人，量宽足以得人，身先足以率人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zfs16xc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zfs16xc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vl72oxr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vl72oxr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，不如一忍。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8roasvw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8roasvw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-keijazz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-keijazz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功名半纸，风雪千山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ls6ce89","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ls6ce89","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0x509n9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0x509n9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"井以甘竭，李以苦成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lwau27p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lwau27p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4ci0ra0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4ci0ra0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠君明月满前溪，直到西湖畔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9pjacty","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9pjacty","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-20hi7yn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-20hi7yn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道虽迩(ěr)，不行不至；事虽小，不为不成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3o671dl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3o671dl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sj8uyua","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sj8uyua","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为草当作兰，为木当作松。兰秋香风远，松寒不改容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uxr62so","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uxr62so","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hwz04to","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hwz04to","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用威者不轻怒，善用恩者不妄施。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9elcmtf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9elcmtf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-31cd3wb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-31cd3wb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马先驯而后求良，人先信而后求能。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-evj5li0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-evj5li0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w8hmnqv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w8hmnqv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cr8oaew","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cr8oaew","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tmt61he","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tmt61he","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人要是不能从过程中体味幸福和快乐，生命就成了一场荒诞的苦役。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-quv6ktz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-quv6ktz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zdsth4m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zdsth4m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君王城上竖降旗，妾在深宫那得知？十四万人齐解甲，更无一个是男儿！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-aad606o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aad606o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3csrrqf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3csrrqf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，避其锐气，击其惰归，此治气者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-07hiwoq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-07hiwoq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-toglk0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-toglk0r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政入万山围子里，一山放出一山拦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-15bm6hd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-15bm6hd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mc6ykj7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mc6ykj7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地者万物之逆旅也；光阴者百代之过客也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v32j291","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v32j291","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lymissv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lymissv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽不能至，心向往之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-480fes0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-480fes0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-65b3e9o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-65b3e9o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高者未必贤，下者未必愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6uaka8w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6uaka8w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9q5xy8l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9q5xy8l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与朋友交游，须将他们好处留心学来，方能受益；对圣贤言语，必要我平时照样行去，才算读书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-67aybqf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-67aybqf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-n912yo2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n912yo2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二人同心，其利断金；同心之言，其臭(xiù)如兰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mfyf4ip","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mfyf4ip","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-35mnxvp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-35mnxvp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子不蔽人之美，不言人之恶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vnn9o88","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vnn9o88","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yhi7068","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yhi7068","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-b1da2uc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b1da2uc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mdvunqv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mdvunqv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道德用于自律时好过一切法律，用于律他时坏过一切私刑！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5w8m1co","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5w8m1co","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i5umzb1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i5umzb1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山高自有客行路，水深自有渡船人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yiit1gl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yiit1gl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j4p5vac","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j4p5vac","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d7j2m8c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d7j2m8c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u9h0t1d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u9h0t1d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不忘初心，方得始终。初心易得，始终难守。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w00z7ty","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w00z7ty","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4ff5ire","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4ff5ire","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不迁怒，不贰过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mmv01yo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mmv01yo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-puycd69","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-puycd69","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用兵之法，十则围之，五则攻之，倍则分之，敌则能战之，少则能逃之，不若则能避之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lb87o71","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lb87o71","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3dulq85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3dulq85","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"越自尊大，越见器小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m5zp6l8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m5zp6l8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mfzheq7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mfzheq7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浮云一别后，流水十年间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kd29qjm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kd29qjm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s54ogkl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s54ogkl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穆勒 ：个人的自由，以不侵犯他人的自由为自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kdqp6fh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kdqp6fh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nr1rb4e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nr1rb4e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小舟从此逝，江海寄余生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-us3szsn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-us3szsn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-issfjbq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-issfjbq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云山苍苍，江水泱泱，先生之风，山高水长！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ha045tu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ha045tu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lr0r7un","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lr0r7un","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"行远道者假于车，济江海者因于舟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-36i6gjb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-36i6gjb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4361tur","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4361tur","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cn46z41","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cn46z41","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tux7dp7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tux7dp7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立志欲坚不欲锐，成功在久不在速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qqemqxr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qqemqxr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-818rltb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-818rltb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-szy4spi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-szy4spi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tbh6joe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tbh6joe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布伦南：手头上有点钱的人认为爱是世界上最重要的东西，而穷人则明白世界上最重要的是金钱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-i9s74ny","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i9s74ny","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bi0ur4x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bi0ur4x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"冯至《十四行集》：我们准备着，深深地领受，那些意想不到的奇迹。在漫长的岁月里，忽然有彗星的出现，狂风乍起。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z0rxa4k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z0rxa4k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qf4kfvx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qf4kfvx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"疾风怒雨，禽鸟戚戚；霁月光风，草木欣欣。天地不可一日无和气，人心不可一日无喜神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sw7zxmi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sw7zxmi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-98kg5z4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-98kg5z4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫之高华，只在于道德气节。鄙夫之炫耀，但求诸服饰起居。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x2fq022","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x2fq022","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nptb7l4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nptb7l4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"甘井近竭，招木近伐。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-83o350g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-83o350g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dcwcqh9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dcwcqh9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，屈人之兵而非战也，拔人之城而非攻也，毁人之国而非久也，必以全争于天下。故兵不顿而利可全，此谋攻之法也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qsi61pf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qsi61pf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-k3kc9uk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k3kc9uk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你吞并一切，像远方，像大海，像时间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bm7kbvs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bm7kbvs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-by6yzoe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-by6yzoe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"挟取笔端风雨，快写胸中丘壑，不肯下樊笼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5ldhcu2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5ldhcu2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-asc7w69","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-asc7w69","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴尔扎克：一星陨落，黯淡不了星空灿烂；一花凋零，荒芜不了整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k0vxmbe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k0vxmbe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tebqqg0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tebqqg0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"伯修斯：在所有不幸中，最不幸的事是曾经幸福过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-u2z0ajj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u2z0ajj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7wy18z2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7wy18z2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草萤有耀终非火，荷露虽团岂是珠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mjcbwbj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mjcbwbj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-itb312s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-itb312s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"耳闻之不如目见之，目见之不如足践之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-drbysgb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-drbysgb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nst9unp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nst9unp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卖花担上，买得一枝春欲放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4rb056e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4rb056e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-00nt5ld","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-00nt5ld","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亭亭山上松，瑟(sè)瑟谷中风。风声一何盛，松枝一何劲。冰霜正惨凄，终岁常端正。岂不罹(lí)凝寒，松柏有本性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2bithry","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2bithry","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6wyd6s2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6wyd6s2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好问则裕，自用则小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jnq8s99","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jnq8s99","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5w4sjfv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5w4sjfv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雾失楼台，月迷津渡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lxc2ec7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lxc2ec7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-05xvbt9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-05xvbt9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：世界以痛吻我，我也要报之以歌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-52v611p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-52v611p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z531ue0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z531ue0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人之诺诺，不如一士之谔谔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-r3u6gnj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r3u6gnj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8mk8mlg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8mk8mlg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早岁读书无甚解，晚年省事有奇功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7ex7w3i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ex7w3i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dflth27","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dflth27","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你所浪费的今天，是昨天死去的人奢望的明天；你所厌恶的现在，是未来的你回不去的曾经。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2188k6y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2188k6y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9i68mpk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9i68mpk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：有很多人常常抱怨没有机会，其实没有机会本身亦是一个机会：一个锻炼自己耐力和充分积蓄自己力量的机会。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zu9ls4w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zu9ls4w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9f5zjvc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9f5zjvc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世界让我遍体鳞伤，但伤口长出的却是翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ouvg159","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ouvg159","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5r2fkcg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5r2fkcg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡战者，以正合，以奇胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4jerkvz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4jerkvz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-aqyrnxb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aqyrnxb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方其中，圆其外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7b6m9mx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7b6m9mx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cdhm8z1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cdhm8z1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独学而无友，则孤陋而寡闻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-alyvl5b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-alyvl5b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-klul2ud","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-klul2ud","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：苦难既然把我推到了悬崖的边缘，那么就让我在这悬崖的边缘坐下来，顺便看看悬崖下的流岚雾霭，唱支歌给你听。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l1zg6o4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l1zg6o4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vqztw9v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vqztw9v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国虽大，好战必亡；天下虽安，忘战必危。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3ffg31e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3ffg31e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gqoyntl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gqoyntl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：每个冬天的句号都是春暖花开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m5jjcnh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m5jjcnh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9uoff0w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9uoff0w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百里趋利，兵家所忌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gvfs92t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gvfs92t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yoe87vd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yoe87vd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李大钊：谁对时间越吝啬，时间对谁越慷慨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-awub8v8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-awub8v8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v8b4scj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v8b4scj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粗缯大布裹生涯，腹有诗书气自华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3ljgtxu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3ljgtxu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xlpao14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xlpao14","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ay9r299","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ay9r299","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tw7l7te","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tw7l7te","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"慈不掌兵，情不立事，义不理财，善不为官。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y3s3akd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y3s3akd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-se6ucgo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-se6ucgo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大巧在所不为，大智在所不虑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yjiuhdb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yjiuhdb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jl6g6ou","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jl6g6ou","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海到尽头天作岸，山登绝顶我为峰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-63ymcsc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-63ymcsc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2lbb5hn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2lbb5hn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨之为物，能令昼短，能令夜长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-glyu7wd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-glyu7wd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v867itn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v867itn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善出奇者，无穷如天地，不竭如江海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ntpzmlx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ntpzmlx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1kff6rj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1kff6rj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫行事，当磊磊落落，如日月皎然。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8vwwv5e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8vwwv5e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5jm0n48","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5jm0n48","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者行之始，行者知之成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-43rgbok","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-43rgbok","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6zun142","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6zun142","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者不以短击长，而以长击短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-np9f9uq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-np9f9uq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-byuahq9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-byuahq9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"振衣千仞冈，濯足万里流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9mrbsuh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9mrbsuh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dmwvu1o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dmwvu1o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：你今天受的苦、吃的亏、担的责、扛的罪、忍的痛，到最后都会变成光，照亮你的路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x5u36ve","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x5u36ve","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ubta40t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ubta40t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张而不弛，文武弗能也；弛而不张，文武弗为也。一张一弛，文武之道也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bxx3ons","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bxx3ons","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j9bx9rv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j9bx9rv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善为士者，不武；善战者，不怒；善胜敌者，不与；善用人者，为之下。是谓不争之德，是谓用人之力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tt6ftno","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tt6ftno","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lt1ok48","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lt1ok48","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中心藏之，何日忘之！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-09nizw0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-09nizw0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4p30ya5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4p30ya5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：没有比脚更长的路，没有比人更高的山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xds23ec","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xds23ec","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2svfv3h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2svfv3h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：才能是在寂静中造就，而品格则是在世间汹涌波涛中形成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j50p9fi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j50p9fi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-x77aqdr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x77aqdr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有迷魂招不得，雄鸡一声天下白。少年心事当拏云，谁念幽寒坐呜呃。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c5ctdmq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c5ctdmq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4pallgz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4pallgz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尺之木必有节目，寸之玉必有瑕疵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-of42svh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-of42svh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gzrbofx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gzrbofx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曾国藩：天下古今之庸人，皆以一惰字致败；天下古今之才人，皆以一傲字致败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-a88fe4b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a88fe4b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-r62i7m3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r62i7m3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"培根：当你孤独寂寞时，阅读可以消遣。当你高谈阔论时，知识可供装饰。当你处世行事时，正确运用知识意味着力量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9wvxc5g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9wvxc5g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xntob80","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xntob80","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"辅车相依，唇亡齿寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3z837lv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3z837lv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ythg3cy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ythg3cy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"池田大作：荣誉有如萤虫之火，在黑暗的夜空里，它放着光，显示出美丽，极其可贵。但是靠近一看，立刻就会明白它是何等的软弱无力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xs1u33h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xs1u33h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fmzjcz5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fmzjcz5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：谁终将声震人间，必长久深自缄默；谁终将点燃闪电，必长久如云漂泊。我的时代还没有到来，有的人死后方生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-g6bnrkc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g6bnrkc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g24liae","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g24liae","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"三毛：梦想，可以天花乱坠；理想，是我们一步一个脚印踩出来的坎坷道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lyl09bm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lyl09bm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8bec2lz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8bec2lz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志不可一日坠，心不可一日放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ujdq6bk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ujdq6bk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mug6nwp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mug6nwp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一双冷眼看世人，满腔热血酬知己。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3119sn7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3119sn7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-769s3s2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-769s3s2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗翔：误解是人生常态，理解是稀缺的例外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4q66r2n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4q66r2n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i5vdvvf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i5vdvvf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杀人亦有限，列国自有疆。苟能制侵陵，岂在多杀伤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ej18qrj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ej18qrj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-b20bori","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b20bori","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝闻道，夕死可矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-860ujmd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-860ujmd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hrjflf4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hrjflf4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫四方志，安可辞固穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-28vko2a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-28vko2a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o3am5h0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o3am5h0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粪虫至秽变为蝉，而饮露于秋风；腐草无光化为荧，而耀采于夏月。故知洁常自污出，明每从暗生也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qfoq9bf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qfoq9bf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tpm2zqt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tpm2zqt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"物以稀为贵，情因老更慈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-q8xjntb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q8xjntb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-baziejv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-baziejv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y91p1wm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y91p1wm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7d5r07f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7d5r07f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能受谏，安能谏人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mubnaax","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mubnaax","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sua2a1j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sua2a1j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生岂草木，寒暑移此心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cp8vavc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cp8vavc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8e7goqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8e7goqh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫当容人，勿为人所容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cro2jj2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cro2jj2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ro9ftgd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ro9ftgd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不为无益之事，何以悦有涯之生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xmv7ce7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xmv7ce7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9c37zot","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9c37zot","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海棠未雨，梨花先雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rkcsend","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rkcsend","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-200y0le","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-200y0le","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地薄者大木不产，水浅者大鱼不游。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-r7t49zo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r7t49zo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qfsb36b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qfsb36b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"忧勤是美德，太苦则无以适性怡情；淡泊是高风，太枯则无以济人利物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4eo6gbg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4eo6gbg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2aeylmh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2aeylmh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书为身上之用，而人以为纸上之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-140odfg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-140odfg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tfkadpz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tfkadpz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天可补，海可填，南山可移。日月既往，不可复追。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ccawb2j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ccawb2j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kdbxyeo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kdbxyeo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼布尔：请赐予我平静，去接受我无法改变的；给予我勇气，去改变我能改变的；赐我智慧，分辨这两者的区别。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-enp9ncq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-enp9ncq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yhcbohn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yhcbohn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"腹中贮书一万卷，不肯低头在草莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qea89j3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qea89j3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3ypeln8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3ypeln8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"须知少日拏云志，曾许人间第一流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ezmiadq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ezmiadq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mv4cbn4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mv4cbn4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间的步伐有三种：未来姗姗来迟，现在像箭一样飞逝，过去永远静立不动。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t141qwg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t141qwg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a26w3er","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a26w3er","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天若无雪霜，青松不如草。地若无山川，何人重平道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2g5ui1f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2g5ui1f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qarmcwo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qarmcwo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡心所向，素履所往，生如逆旅，一苇以航。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tl67nl9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tl67nl9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-16erepl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-16erepl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓事宜急干，敏则有功；急事宜缓办，忙则多错。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-117l540","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-117l540","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-n0365u6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n0365u6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众口铄金，积毁销骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-u0r9uwx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u0r9uwx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m9al9pb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m9al9pb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春日迟迟，卉木萋萋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lv3l1a8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lv3l1a8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2ulfqjc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2ulfqjc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若有恒何必三更眠五更起，最无益莫过一日曝十日寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0nizdh1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0nizdh1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-crf9dz1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-crf9dz1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-o69sgfe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o69sgfe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1hm1w9q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1hm1w9q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人之相知，贵相知心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rahcua9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rahcua9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5pfv929","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5pfv929","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桃李春风一杯酒，江湖夜雨十年灯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oixs7yn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oixs7yn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vpj9rx9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vpj9rx9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"东风知我欲山行，吹断檐间积雨声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hzbomb6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hzbomb6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s2jfqx7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s2jfqx7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桐花万里丹山路，雏凤清于老凤声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7tyww1n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7tyww1n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nkombvj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nkombvj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不能设计，你只能面对。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rboqo2e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rboqo2e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lx83vl1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lx83vl1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地不仁，以万物为刍狗；圣人不仁，以百姓为刍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-72jak99","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-72jak99","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7tou62w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7tou62w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心随长风去，吹散万里云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9gywgj4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9gywgj4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hafsdf0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hafsdf0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见面怜清瘦，呼儿问苦辛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bldkazf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bldkazf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hpwqsqy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hpwqsqy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查尔斯·A·比尔德：当天空黑暗到一定程度，星辰就会熠熠生辉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-o33ix1o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o33ix1o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rkj68b2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rkj68b2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中何以赠君别，惟有青青松树枝。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y9m1r6d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y9m1r6d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lg37nly","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lg37nly","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏必加于有功，刑必断于有罪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yrwryla","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yrwryla","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4s33mgt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4s33mgt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规小节者不能成荣名，恶小耻者不能立大功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ooubc8z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ooubc8z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-onqzt6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-onqzt6p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"沈从文：聪明人要理解生活，愚蠢人要习惯生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uhmw0vd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uhmw0vd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6duioje","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6duioje","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"康德：世界上有两件东西能震撼人们的心灵：一件是我们心中崇高的道德标准；另一件是我们头顶上灿烂的星空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-x0npzah","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x0npzah","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tw73nlg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tw73nlg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叔本华：财富就像海水，饮得越多，渴得越厉害。名望实际上也是如此。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pvjgkhb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pvjgkhb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h7js06v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h7js06v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵者，国之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4e6x8us","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4e6x8us","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hmme8e3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hmme8e3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵无常势，水无常形，能因敌变化而取胜者，谓之神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fev8yk9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fev8yk9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y9zk82v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y9zk82v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何物动人二月杏花八月桂，有谁催我三更灯火五更鸡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nmwy35z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nmwy35z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6toofpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6toofpr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自古骄兵多致败，从来轻敌少成功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0i5sf8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0i5sf8f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ufnazdr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ufnazdr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知往日所往之非，则学日进矣；见世人可取者多，则德日进矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nrjv6r7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nrjv6r7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1mu7gzv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1mu7gzv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马太福音：凡有的，还要加倍给他，叫他有余；没有的，连他剩余的也要夺过来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-clf8k9x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-clf8k9x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ick7v9m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ick7v9m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风流不在谈锋胜，袖手无言味最长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gobcrca","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gobcrca","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ing77v2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ing77v2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恻隐之心，人皆有之；羞恶之心，人皆有之；恭敬之心，人皆有之；是非之心，人皆有之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vl5jgjs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vl5jgjs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6qf29oy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6qf29oy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qcu21hx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qcu21hx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d5pk3wc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d5pk3wc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"已识乾坤大，犹怜草木青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tt1foux","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tt1foux","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z1jtp78","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z1jtp78","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鹏北海，凤朝阳。又携书剑路茫茫。明年此日青云上，却笑人间举子忙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8cyrmoi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8cyrmoi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7srl2p0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7srl2p0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝饮木兰之坠露兮，夕餐秋菊之落英。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ex0hhw7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ex0hhw7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0ryz5gr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0ryz5gr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人同心则得千人之力，万人异心则无一人之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1d28stb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1d28stb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5o3i10k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5o3i10k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出其所不趋，趋其所不意。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jt2ni6v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jt2ni6v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-o0fr93j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o0fr93j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"戒骄风清月朗，除躁海阔天空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vkkgdbe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vkkgdbe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i2jyd3t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i2jyd3t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何时杖尔看南雪，我与梅花两白头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-495viks","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-495viks","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-119jyby","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-119jyby","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一时宠利有尽，千秋青史难欺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ejk9axi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ejk9axi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e1jh6zq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e1jh6zq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山川异域，风月同天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2ikvwa7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2ikvwa7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8k94m0g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8k94m0g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白石似玉，奸佞似贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jr5u71e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jr5u71e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wmszpp7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wmszpp7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深厚的教养所集成的勇猛，远远胜过无知无情者的鲁莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1zglk9u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1zglk9u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1sg6psq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1sg6psq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"积财千万，不如薄技在身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cu7jd0m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cu7jd0m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jtsroe2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jtsroe2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：生活总是让我们遍体鳞伤，但到后来，那些受伤的地方一定会变成我们最强壮的地方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uvq5271","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uvq5271","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e0xuqso","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e0xuqso","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当年不肯嫁春风，无端却被秋风误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ogkyw4s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ogkyw4s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dsrwrlf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dsrwrlf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良辰美景奈何天，赏心乐事谁家院。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d6mezsd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d6mezsd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-duukp0g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-duukp0g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"唤起一天明月，照我满怀冰雪，浩荡百川流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ngaoy9a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ngaoy9a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bbbtidz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bbbtidz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"休对故人思故国，且将新火试新茶。诗酒趁年华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qkiobsg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qkiobsg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8vc359y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8vc359y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：那些听不见音乐的人，认为那些跳舞的人疯了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ylc2c5l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ylc2c5l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sgr9yyw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sgr9yyw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：其实人跟树是一样的，越是向往高处的阳光，它的根就越要伸向黑暗的地底。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mexgs0g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mexgs0g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7lwirfc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7lwirfc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉可碎而不可改其白，竹可焚而不可毁其节。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9d7ab69","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9d7ab69","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7ytap6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ytap6j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"南风吹其心，摇摇为谁吐？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7vvw5rc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7vvw5rc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6aj0pbb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6aj0pbb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴金：希望是人生之需要。人如没有希望，何异江河干涸了流水？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d9dpzjo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d9dpzjo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zyepz6z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zyepz6z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷不失义，达不离道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-87xe4pe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-87xe4pe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pj606le","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pj606le","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为者常成，行者常至。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hb8l3p8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hb8l3p8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lbom4k0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lbom4k0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"青云当自致，何必求知音？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xhvlag9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xhvlag9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7l50b9c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7l50b9c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"争名者于朝，争利者于市。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5mwwm45","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5mwwm45","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-28k6kqp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-28k6kqp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天上浮云如白衣，斯须变幻如苍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7ny3sml","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ny3sml","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pfhlztf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pfhlztf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莺花犹怕春光老，岂可教人枉度春？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-o95hovr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-o95hovr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3u8os0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3u8os0r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生芳秽有千载，世上荣枯无百年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-b67khak","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b67khak","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2k5gg8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2k5gg8u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你的欢乐和悲哀变大的时候，世界就变小了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qimr7q0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qimr7q0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0mk76bu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0mk76bu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故将有五危，必死可杀，必生可虏，忿速可侮，廉洁可辱，爱民可烦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-28k8aha","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-28k8aha","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-58fgxzf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-58fgxzf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纵使文章惊海内，纸上苍生而已。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nz5hlr6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nz5hlr6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4i1q394","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4i1q394","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死生契阔，与子成说。执子之手，与子偕老。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ozup5w3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ozup5w3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gld4jo9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gld4jo9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兼听则明，偏信则暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s8597s5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s8597s5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fhvm55b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fhvm55b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"弃燕雀小志，作鸿鹄高翔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rofcg1y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rofcg1y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7y7avws","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7y7avws","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"眼界要阔，遍历名山大川；度量要宏，熟读五经诸史。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-40dmh3d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-40dmh3d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ivu64iy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ivu64iy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地存肝胆，江山阅鬓华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-clsllxj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-clsllxj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4q29sdu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4q29sdu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不相见，动如参与商。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mzm16hp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mzm16hp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-c8akywf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c8akywf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莫道君行早，更有早行人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xwjflac","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xwjflac","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mb05dq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mb05dq5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大人者，不失其赤子之心者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-f4v7pbj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f4v7pbj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zef1w6o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zef1w6o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"英雄者，胸怀大志，腹有良谋，有包藏宇宙之机，吞吐天地之志者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nsds75w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nsds75w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j0x22qh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j0x22qh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪里温柔，水边明秀，不借春工力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hmt1il7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hmt1il7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-60jprtv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-60jprtv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良言一句三冬暖，恶语伤人六月寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ttav55b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ttav55b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g69vmy5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g69vmy5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学如弓弩，才如箭镞。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1ni4l8r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1ni4l8r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4tfii1o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4tfii1o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人不读书，其犹夜行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-alkhwew","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-alkhwew","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g9dukkn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g9dukkn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷猿奔林，岂暇择木！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ihela74","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ihela74","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0m9qirg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0m9qirg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令在必信，法在必行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zxmu8u9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zxmu8u9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7e9wp8w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7e9wp8w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其疾如风，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不动如山，难知如阴，动如雷震。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4gp9g8k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4gp9g8k","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-epgwrh1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-epgwrh1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-224zmcj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-224zmcj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f4mv7h8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f4mv7h8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我亦飘零久！十年来，深恩负尽，死生师友。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vvm27g4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vvm27g4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5gsiwbv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5gsiwbv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"板凳要坐十年冷，文章不写一句空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3ob5k3o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3ob5k3o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9twmtp6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9twmtp6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有心为善，虽善不赏；无心为恶，虽恶不罚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-aisxrsf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aisxrsf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-go1zlgb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-go1zlgb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不目见口问，不能尽知也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4fy0c0w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4fy0c0w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ga5k5uj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ga5k5uj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一年之计，莫如树谷；十年之计，莫如树木；终身之计，莫如树人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tl249c3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tl249c3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tzmd4s1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tzmd4s1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不因幸运而故步自封，不因厄运而一蹶不振。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0oa8v81","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0oa8v81","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5es6td7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5es6td7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良弓难张，然可以及高入深；良马难乘，然可以任重致远。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lrzqy13","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lrzqy13","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kh5736f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kh5736f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上兵伐谋，其次伐交，其次伐兵，其下攻城。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-am19yox","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-am19yox","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a8uct68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a8uct68","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志合者不以山海为远，道乖者不以咫尺为近。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yba78s8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yba78s8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cihx29i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cihx29i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海水梦悠悠，君愁我亦愁。南风知我意，吹梦到西洲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-n5jliqg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n5jliqg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gb5b1zz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gb5b1zz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不幸者常常愿意同幸运者相比，抱怨自己的运气。幸运者常常不愿同不幸者相比，相信自己的努力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5vfy82e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5vfy82e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6liv7jw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6liv7jw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怯生于勇，弱生于强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m1kqd9i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m1kqd9i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q4afh8h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q4afh8h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贵上极则反贱，贱下极则反贵。贵出如粪土，贱取如珠玉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gch1bkq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gch1bkq","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uiaqys1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uiaqys1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有志者事竟成破釜沉舟百二秦关终属楚，苦心人天不负卧薪尝胆三千越甲可吞吴。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-h9fq8m9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h9fq8m9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e2ql0wg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e2ql0wg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔日之得不足以自衿，今日之成不容以自限。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lkwmaax","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lkwmaax","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-smk8ru7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-smk8ru7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不善操舟者，恶河之曲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-slt10bb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-slt10bb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-b7haj8i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b7haj8i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操千曲而后晓声，观千剑而后识器。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-92q54z4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-92q54z4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ykx8c65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ykx8c65","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长安何处在，只在马蹄下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cv782tt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cv782tt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i6pp1cu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i6pp1cu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人情阅尽秋云厚，世事经多蜀道平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-pm1tlnd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pm1tlnd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0t68nlu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0t68nlu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志行万里者，不中道而辍足。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zjdrm5m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zjdrm5m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-emgz9yv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-emgz9yv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交友须带三分侠气，做人要存一点素心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7arx4z1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7arx4z1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a7j237a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a7j237a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿不展风云志，空负天生八尺躯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qpl6rlf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qpl6rlf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qfz7s6f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qfz7s6f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"愿作远方兽，步步比肩行。愿作深山木，枝枝连理生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y8xg01i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y8xg01i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5hc6rff","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5hc6rff","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵不厌诈，将贵知机。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kf36rx2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kf36rx2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9upea09","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9upea09","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上士闻道，勤而行之；中士闻道，若存若亡；下士闻道，大笑之。不笑不足以为道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-e5koxws","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e5koxws","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h70gfbl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h70gfbl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子慎始，差若毫厘，缪以千里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-51fkmn1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-51fkmn1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e0d2jv1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e0d2jv1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古来多被虚名误，宁负虚名身莫负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p7zmo0a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p7zmo0a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4zwjxcx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4zwjxcx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我志在寥阔，畴昔梦登天。摩挲素月，俯仰已千年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gfs1eda","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gfs1eda","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-91nvl3d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-91nvl3d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们每个人出生的时候，并非是两手空空，而是捏了一张生命的借记卡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7ia22kh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ia22kh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-caq2fex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-caq2fex","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好风凭借力，送我上青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sru88wn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sru88wn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cyulpu4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cyulpu4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉在山而草木润，渊生珠而崖不枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p62j7z9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p62j7z9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-obvao2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-obvao2g","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学之染人，甚于丹青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jbncnsf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jbncnsf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0uo4pt0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0uo4pt0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地有万古，此身不再得；人生只百年，此日最易过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4bf9rzt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4bf9rzt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tnze3px","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tnze3px","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十有九人堪白眼，百无一用是书生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bof1iqi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bof1iqi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-p6m8kar","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p6m8kar","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫志四海，万里犹比邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fkbgz0a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fkbgz0a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-67zad91","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-67zad91","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仗义每多屠狗辈，负心多是读书人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zjcoa9w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zjcoa9w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-706raox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-706raox","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"涓涓不塞，将为江河。荧荧不救，炎炎奈何。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v7s36qc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v7s36qc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tmobeb8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tmobeb8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如寄，多忧何为？今我不乐，岁月如驰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-59ww4s3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-59ww4s3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tf9i96t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tf9i96t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天行有常，不为尧存，不为桀亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-t7jkqr1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-t7jkqr1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-po296u6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-po296u6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书志在圣贤，非徒科第；为官心存君国，岂计身家？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ztfhv0s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ztfhv0s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3sld3it","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3sld3it","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少而好学，如日出之阳；壮而好学，如日中之光；老而好学，如秉烛之明。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9by7ivs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9by7ivs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yz8tb00","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yz8tb00","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纪伯伦：不要因为走得太远而忘记为什么出发。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ihbx91e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ihbx91e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pd85cv1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pd85cv1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用赏者贵信，用罚者贵必。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w8mcymn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w8mcymn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l7kdeic","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l7kdeic","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"傲不可长，欲不可纵，乐不可极，志不可满。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4r65e62","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4r65e62","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i4pmnj8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i4pmnj8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子爱财，取之有道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-bqyiddb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bqyiddb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-lngoiie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lngoiie","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"余光中：敢在时间里自焚的人，必在永恒里结晶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v7ftnub","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v7ftnub","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-a5idz46","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a5idz46","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主不可以怒而兴师，将不可以愠而致战；合于利而动，不合于利而止。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l74avdu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l74avdu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q362zs1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q362zs1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uvofdzx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uvofdzx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v8csf01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v8csf01","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海子：永远是这样，风后面是风，天空上面是天空，道路前面还是道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tgaki90","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tgaki90","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-37kuyoi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-37kuyoi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：如果你抑郁了，说明你活在过去；如果你焦虑了，说明你活在未来；如果你平静了，才说明你活在现在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2kjpl30","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2kjpl30","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pjc0go3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pjc0go3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对愁人勿乐，对哭人勿笑，对失意人勿矜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3wto5oo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3wto5oo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e57xwsz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e57xwsz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知胜有五：知可以战与不可以战者胜，识众寡之用者胜，上下同欲者胜，以虞待不虞者胜，将能而君不御者胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-703wunn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-703wunn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bl7hjwm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bl7hjwm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钝学累功，不妨精熟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ueloc0f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ueloc0f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fs6bmxx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fs6bmxx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"闭门即是深山，读书随处净土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-le1lqro","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-le1lqro","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-959cg9t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-959cg9t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人非生而知之者，孰能无惑?惑而不从师，其为惑也，终不解矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hfbzmg3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hfbzmg3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-egtpo7o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-egtpo7o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见胜不过众人之所知，非善之善者也；战胜而天下曰善，非善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-satggc8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-satggc8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g02cfjh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g02cfjh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"折芦花赠远，零落一身秋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-giqf99c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-giqf99c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kemv4qj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kemv4qj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老骥伏枥志千里，短锥处囊半寸锋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-233p1lz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-233p1lz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zu1kdiu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zu1kdiu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只要厄运打不垮信念，希望之光就会驱散绝望之云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-llo9po2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-llo9po2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3ccgbo0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3ccgbo0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以势交者，势尽则疏，以利合者，利尽则散。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qqw7zye","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qqw7zye","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vnoy9mk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vnoy9mk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如月之恒，如日之升。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-duv2btx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-duv2btx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-26vydxg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-26vydxg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合军聚众，务在激气。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wzrbz5q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wzrbz5q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ktmwhs7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ktmwhs7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贝尔纳：构成我们学习最大障碍的是已知的东西，而不是未知的东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-6r4t7se","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6r4t7se","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-klrtct7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-klrtct7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"约瑟夫·海勒《第二十二条军规》：任何值得为它而死的东西，肯定值得为它而生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-g8xy9u6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g8xy9u6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-74acbq7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-74acbq7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云路鹏程九万里，雪窗萤火二十年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tvedy2h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tvedy2h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mrj15pl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mrj15pl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"华而不实，怨之所聚也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0vdo51n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0vdo51n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3teae57","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3teae57","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"精卫衔微木，将以填沧海；刑天舞干戚，猛志固常在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-d5zipuz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d5zipuz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ko9a595","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ko9a595","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z07jtdv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z07jtdv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mn3j09c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mn3j09c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丹青不知老将至，富贵于我如浮云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-35ago9d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-35ago9d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xlhaaod","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xlhaaod","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"胡适：凡富于创造性的人必敏于模仿，凡不善于模仿的人决不能创造。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0edgjey","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0edgjey","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g7p9yps","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g7p9yps","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"节义傲青云，文章高白雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4rzfhat","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4rzfhat","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3pey4yo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3pey4yo","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提得起，放得下，算得到，做得完，看得破，撇得开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zat8mhn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zat8mhn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vzbak32","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vzbak32","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪曾祺：一定要爱着点什么，恰似草木对光阴的钟情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hrltnl9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hrltnl9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-36objzs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-36objzs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有所念人，隔在远远乡。我有所感事，结在深深肠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yxya3j2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yxya3j2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q39i13y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q39i13y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草不谢荣于春风，木不怨落于秋天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yanr01m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yanr01m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gzobb6w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gzobb6w","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一竹一兰一石，有节有香有骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oe4rmee","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oe4rmee","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-awtez49","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-awtez49","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"笔落惊风雨，诗成泣鬼神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vuoxmdx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vuoxmdx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0bdz5cd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0bdz5cd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合抱之木，生于毫末；九层之台，起于累土；千里之行，始于足下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fle1z4j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fle1z4j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bvo50kw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bvo50kw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山不让尘，川不辞盈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3rdti75","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3rdti75","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-q1taae0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q1taae0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"皑如山上雪，皎若云间月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9i7jvec","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9i7jvec","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7upsw6c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7upsw6c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客子光阴诗卷里，杏花消息雨声中。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iin8bt7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iin8bt7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pfltnq1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pfltnq1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：我们的眼睛就是我们的监狱，而目光所及之处就是监狱的围墙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-52eqv2z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-52eqv2z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7gt5t4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7gt5t4b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中送炭人间少，锦上添花世上多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vz9q0fa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vz9q0fa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m5gdhq1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m5gdhq1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蒲柳之姿，望秋而落；松柏之质，经霜弥茂。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w2ewo3e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w2ewo3e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kj56owj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kj56owj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不戚戚于贫贱，不汲汲于富贵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nrdem4x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nrdem4x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-98xr2ol","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-98xr2ol","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"门前红叶地，不扫待知音。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hnb9562","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hnb9562","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xp4prev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xp4prev","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"村上春树：这个世界上根本没有正确的选择，我们只不过是要努力奋斗，使当初的选择变得正确。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4lhh21z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4lhh21z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-naa0uc8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-naa0uc8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缘木求鱼，煎水作冰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mpn6dif","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mpn6dif","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1vnvjni","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1vnvjni","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟日新，日日新，又日新。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jvai0jp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jvai0jp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bcwgcax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bcwgcax","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贫无可奈惟求俭，拙亦何妨只要勤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-20b6qy9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-20b6qy9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5az3dyg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5az3dyg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文章千古事，得失寸心知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v76mw7z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v76mw7z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mv3htws","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mv3htws","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨滴能击穿石头，并不是下落的速度快，而是因为掉落在石头上的次数多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mok7569","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mok7569","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7c1au91","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7c1au91","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人有逆天之时，天无绝人之路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1smki3m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1smki3m","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s2svuzh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s2svuzh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宁为宇宙闲吟客，怕作乾坤窃禄人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mwfrghf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mwfrghf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-pu3m982","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-pu3m982","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"受光于隙见一床，受光于窗见室央，受光于庭户见一堂，受光于天下照四方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-zahaj1a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zahaj1a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g3m8d26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g3m8d26","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马不可以服重，牛不可以追速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gvpdn28","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gvpdn28","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7ivudwk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7ivudwk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改过不吝，从善如流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sfrm8g0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sfrm8g0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bvta2um","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bvta2um","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚负凌云万丈才，一生襟抱未曾开。鸟啼花落人何在，竹死桐枯凤不来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-r9nha1t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r9nha1t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cyq6d5b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cyq6d5b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兰生幽谷，不为莫服而不芳；舟在江海，不为莫乘而不浮；君子行义，不为莫知而止休。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-170n7kh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-170n7kh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w8wdg68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w8wdg68","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一日不思量，也攒眉千度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l2xcsgx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l2xcsgx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-jmzh41p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jmzh41p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"彊弩之极，矢不能穿鲁缟；冲风之末，力不能漂鸿毛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hfpoegg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hfpoegg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-15ci4bj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-15ci4bj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时来天地皆同力，运去英雄不自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8jk9vap","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8jk9vap","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vz8uaak","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vz8uaak","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"倒持干戈，授人以柄。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0z3gq9e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0z3gq9e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vk0rjvx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vk0rjvx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生一世，草生一春。来如风雨，去似微尘。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-p78j853","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-p78j853","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qqme1dy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qqme1dy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪莱：未来不足惧，过往不须泣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y9m84w0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y9m84w0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-y9mszbr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y9mszbr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从善如登，从恶如崩。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l4rvsz8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l4rvsz8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w2nm6ex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w2nm6ex","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春生、夏长、秋收、冬藏，天之正也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iijemqv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iijemqv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9s381p9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9s381p9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前事不忘，后事之师。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ktl6gq9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ktl6gq9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-meq7bli","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-meq7bli","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逢人不说人间事，便是人间无事人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cqaspic","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cqaspic","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-l4o63lz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l4o63lz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"花开花落树之常，能上能下人中强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rxp6pky","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rxp6pky","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-m1v4adp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m1v4adp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立品同白玉，读书到青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8navf1y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8navf1y","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-bkb10q0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-bkb10q0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陀思妥耶夫斯基：爱具体的人，不要爱抽象的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-7lpg5w1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7lpg5w1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ts9dv4z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ts9dv4z","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凭君莫话封侯事，一将功成万骨枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3obobef","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3obobef","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-acjk8y4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-acjk8y4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下皆知美之为美，斯恶已。皆知善之为善，斯不善已。有无相生，难易相成，长短相形，高下相盈，音声相和，前后相随，恒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nnihh77","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nnihh77","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-28ceym3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-28ceym3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子之心事，天青日白，不可使人不知；君子之才华，玉韫珠藏，不可使人易知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ml9b2rn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ml9b2rn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ny4ni6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ny4ni6p","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除掉荒草的最好办法，不是让除完草的土地荒着，而是种上庄稼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vng8tvu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vng8tvu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xjj39e2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xjj39e2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善战者，求之于势，不责于人。故能择人而任势。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fksndzw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fksndzw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v6j6uzd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v6j6uzd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"川泽纳污，所以成其深；山岳藏疾，所以就其大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w1qyhh7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w1qyhh7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-sh8jh5l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sh8jh5l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"覆水不可收，行云难重寻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2lk1gpt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2lk1gpt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-2plb36q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2plb36q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相鼠有皮，人而无仪！人而无仪，不死何为？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oy4yaam","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oy4yaam","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vkupbld","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vkupbld","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qu3747q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qu3747q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zv4mq1o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zv4mq1o","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"狡兔死，走狗烹；飞鸟尽，良弓藏；敌国破，谋臣亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c6fwgl0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c6fwgl0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s5zcpor","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s5zcpor","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马丁·路德·金：我们这一代人终将感到悔恨，不仅仅因为坏人的可憎言行，更因为好人的可怕沉默。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ywvvbpb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ywvvbpb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hh50swb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hh50swb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我本将心向明月，奈何明月照沟渠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m1au5gd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m1au5gd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4qit08r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4qit08r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网；扬汤止沸，不如去火抽薪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4alrz60","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4alrz60","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dd42aa9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dd42aa9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"芳林新叶催陈叶，流水前波让后波。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ebxyurz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ebxyurz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-f961656","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f961656","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日出扶桑一丈高，人间万事细如毛。野夫怒见不平处，磨损胸中万古刀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rdoxwih","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rdoxwih","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tfx4jro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tfx4jro","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：果实的事业是尊贵的，花的事业是甜美的，但是让我做叶的事业吧，叶是谦逊地、专心地垂着绿荫的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8tykysc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8tykysc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9bx6jq0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9bx6jq0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子耻不修，不耻见污。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4oaev18","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4oaev18","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-45155qe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-45155qe","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陶行知：做学问就是要学要问。光学不问，只做到一半；光问不学，也只是一半。又学又问，才是完整的学问。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oqbeahx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oqbeahx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xzoqc52","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xzoqc52","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恶不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-z044e8q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z044e8q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3pvktlu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3pvktlu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众里嫣然通一顾，人间颜色如尘土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-516o04j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-516o04j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fggkz0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fggkz0c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将者，智、信、仁、勇、严也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-sfsbx9t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-sfsbx9t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-xetw5oc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xetw5oc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍：才华是刀刃，辛苦是磨刀石。很锋利的刀刃，若日久不用石磨，也会生锈，成为废物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uqiek1b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uqiek1b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tbr75n4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tbr75n4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少年侠气，交结五都雄。肝胆洞，毛发耸。立谈中，死生同。一诺千金重。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-b193rlv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b193rlv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9010k6x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9010k6x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰 ：一个人的绝对自由是疯狂，一个国家的绝对自由是混乱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-860mzpa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-860mzpa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1vhoa9b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1vhoa9b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学然后知不足，教然后知困。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-g4ybhvw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g4ybhvw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-upwl6p6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-upwl6p6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记人之长，忘人之短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k1w1lio","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k1w1lio","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9vywmnk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9vywmnk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知彼知己者，百战不殆；不知彼而知己，一胜一负，不知彼，不知己，每战必殆。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-uox5m1i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uox5m1i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h994x68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h994x68","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"月缺不改光，剑折不改刚。月缺魄易满，剑折铸复良。势利压山岳，难屈志士肠。男儿自有守，可杀不可苟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-s97uz71","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s97uz71","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dm56rbf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dm56rbf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生贵相知，何必金与钱？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0v1rpyu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0v1rpyu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-biuaae7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-biuaae7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有真才者，必不矜才。有实学者，必不夸学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hpv2j7v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hpv2j7v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-egepdho","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-egepdho","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"薄我货者也，欲与我市者也；訾我行者，欲与我友者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9dv27br","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9dv27br","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i9rno3i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i9rno3i","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风乍起，吹皱一池春水。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ueln75u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ueln75u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-baw891r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-baw891r","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生万事须自为，跬步江山即寥廓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-u0i7xb0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u0i7xb0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-od6aqof","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-od6aqof","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十年磨一剑，霜刃未曾试。今日把示君，谁有不平事？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xxfte7c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xxfte7c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-szkmsa2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-szkmsa2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草木秋死，松柏独在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-76aala9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-76aala9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0iqz1tu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0iqz1tu","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生是一匹马，轻快而健壮的马。人，要像骑手那样大胆而细心地驾驭它。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yzcst42","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yzcst42","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7tr9qbj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7tr9qbj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"水广者鱼大，山高者树修。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8fv1mxv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8fv1mxv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-yojnnog","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yojnnog","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如梦，把梦看得太认真，固然是个大傻瓜；但以为人生如梦，就以为不必认真，也是个头等大傻瓜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-2m8ez7x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-2m8ez7x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-84ukdoa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-84ukdoa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一叶浮萍归大海，为人何处不相逢！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-aqogiw3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aqogiw3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-abba8wh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-abba8wh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"力田不如逢年，善仕不如遇合。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-n7gwil0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-n7gwil0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-j4uz07n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j4uz07n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道路难行钱作马，城池不克酒为兵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-72tourj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-72tourj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-noxpcdh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-noxpcdh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古人云，“读书百遍，其义自见”。谓读得熟，则不待解说，自晓其义也。余尝谓，读书有三到，谓心到，眼到，口到。心不在此，则眼不看仔细，心眼既不专一，却只漫浪诵读，决不能记，记亦不能久也。三到之中，心到最急。心既到矣，眼口岂不到乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ct4vsge","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ct4vsge","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-3yg3uz3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3yg3uz3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知人者智，自知者明。胜人者有力，自胜者强。知足者富。强行者有志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-8wfrfop","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8wfrfop","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qtpic2e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qtpic2e","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"驿寄梅花，鱼传尺素。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wq7nwqg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wq7nwqg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-i701ela","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-i701ela","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自然既极博大，也极残忍，战胜一切，孕育众生。蝼蚁蚍蜉，伟人巨匠，一样在它怀抱中，和光同见。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-f802mb4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-f802mb4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-oxwyzfg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oxwyzfg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：与恶龙缠斗过久，自身亦成恶龙；凝视深渊过久，深渊将回以凝视。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rq8hzua","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rq8hzua","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-muf0xsw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-muf0xsw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天戴其苍，地履其黄，纵有千古，横有八荒，前途似海，来日方长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nwx5nx4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nwx5nx4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cklyjea","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cklyjea","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子坦荡荡，小人长戚戚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-iugy3vt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-iugy3vt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dcdbpxi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dcdbpxi","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心中有丘壑，眉目作山河。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1m96p91","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1m96p91","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ru66eah","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ru66eah","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"寄蜉蝣于天地，渺沧海之一粟。哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-st233jf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-st233jf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vjnwuwy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vjnwuwy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明代思想家袁了凡：昨日种种，譬如昨日死；今日种种，譬如今日生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hj2f92x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hj2f92x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nan3gy8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nan3gy8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黑格尔：只有永远躺在泥坑里的人，才不会再掉进坑里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-idyu3rc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-idyu3rc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-g2f5tbb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g2f5tbb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：每一个不曾起舞的日子都是对生命的辜负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-y229k1x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-y229k1x","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-95wbs2d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-95wbs2d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子在齐闻《韶》，三月不知肉味，曰：‘不图为乐之至于斯也。’"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-acwa7xp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-acwa7xp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dwxp9p9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dwxp9p9","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：命定的局限尽可永在，不屈的挑战却不可须臾或缺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l2j4g01","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l2j4g01","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-5tz3ml5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5tz3ml5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：当我走向你的时候，我原想收获一缕春风，你却给了我整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xnrdtdh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xnrdtdh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-vof1wo1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vof1wo1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：我相信，在群星当中有一颗星星，引领我的生命，穿越不可知的黑暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-96x7fim","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-96x7fim","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wanleyd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wanleyd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：心晴的时候，雨也是晴；心雨的时候，晴也是雨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-egapuay","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-egapuay","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9tj00vk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9tj00vk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聂卫平：遇到顺势而下的时候，就一泻千里；遇到阻碍过不去的时候，就绕一下，但我的目标一直是向前走的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qolx5hh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qolx5hh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-asbmogr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-asbmogr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曼德拉：我没有失败过。要么赢得胜利，要么学到东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cjlm1g6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cjlm1g6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-1vlbxr7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1vlbxr7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间是单程车票，我们只能向前；而记忆是随身行李，始终伴你同行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-v5uqdw3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v5uqdw3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-478s7h4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-478s7h4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"喷泉之所以漂亮，是因为它有压力；瀑布之所以壮观，是因为它没有退路；滴水之所以能穿石，是因为它贵在坚持。一只站在树枝上的鸟，从不害怕树枝会断裂，因为它相信的不是树枝，而是它自己的翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-yohuxxa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-yohuxxa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9612yyj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9612yyj","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"追风赶月莫停留，平芜尽处是春山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l3kukzw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l3kukzw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-fh6hzrd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fh6hzrd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼《浣溪沙·游蕲水清泉寺》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gd5kw33","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gd5kw33","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-gbflulm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gbflulm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朱敦儒《鹧鸪天·西都作》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1dc61j1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1dc61j1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z41kt0l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z41kt0l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杜甫《蜀相》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-rhkisux","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rhkisux","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-qw9qvka","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qw9qvka","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《忆秦娥》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j7i7ffk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j7i7ffk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-knqmyun","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-knqmyun","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《上李邕》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tm90hbw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tm90hbw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-u3fzhas","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-u3fzhas","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游《金错刀行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3mha4xb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3mha4xb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8tt46ox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8tt46ox","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李煜《虞美人》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wu49nyt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wu49nyt","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-aougk1q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-aougk1q","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白居易《琵琶行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qiefmof","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qiefmof","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dafbz2t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dafbz2t","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"礼记《大学》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cchun8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cchun8f","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ntzvjqk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ntzvjqk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"范仲淹《岳阳楼记》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-a5f0dep","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-a5f0dep","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9wnx9c1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9wnx9c1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张若虚《春江花月夜》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ezol811","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ezol811","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-nmcc0im","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nmcc0im","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《侠客行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-l1vyhsn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-l1vyhsn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-c0215iv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c0215iv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗经《无衣》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-3afo8w5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-3afo8w5","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-hxdoxq6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hxdoxq6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗经《木瓜》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-dm9vvd2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dm9vvd2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-65blop1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-65blop1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"王维《终南别业》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4w4v3cg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4w4v3cg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0t0vwcd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0t0vwcd","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李清照《武陵春·春晚》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-mherrp0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mherrp0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-v81iow2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-v81iow2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《宣州谢脁楼饯别校书叔云》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-jgor0id","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-jgor0id","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-z7mr90a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-z7mr90a","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蒋捷《虞美人·听雨》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-tv20743","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tv20743","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wqc8hfl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wqc8hfl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼《前赤壁赋》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ygsohzp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ygsohzp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-0rxxbuy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0rxxbuy","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"欧阳修《醉翁亭记》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-73tkbtx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-73tkbtx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zkhcmxl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zkhcmxl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汉乐府《长歌行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-g7wb58s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-g7wb58s","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-396p5r8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-396p5r8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《滕王阁序》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-nmo74tn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-nmo74tn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-opw4c96","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-opw4c96","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《湖心亭看雪》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-oyjwcvw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-oyjwcvw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ecbf9d8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ecbf9d8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《滕王阁序》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-xgsla57","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-xgsla57","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-dffleek","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-dffleek","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"庄周《北冥有鱼》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-j1arume","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-j1arume","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-h45aoiw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-h45aoiw","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"韩愈 《马说》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-gh91gw7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-gh91gw7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e3spoq2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e3spoq2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"欧阳修《秋声赋》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-wkvw3na","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wkvw3na","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ynwgvli","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ynwgvli","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百里奚之未遇时也，亡虢而虏晋，饭牛于秦，传鬻以五羊之皮。公孙枝得而说之，献诸缪公，三日，请属事焉。缪公曰：“买之五羊之皮而属事焉，无乃为天下笑乎？”公孙枝对曰：“信贤而任之，君之明也；让贤而下之，臣之忠也。君为明君，臣为忠臣。彼信贤，境内将服，敌国且畏，夫谁暇笑哉？”缪公遂用之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4rywodm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4rywodm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-6bvp2c7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-6bvp2c7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"齐桓公好服紫，一国尽服紫。当是时也，五素不得一紫。桓公患之，谓管仲曰：“寡人好服紫，紫贵甚，一国百姓好服紫不已，寡人奈何？”管仲曰：“君欲何不试勿衣紫也，谓左右曰：吾甚恶紫之臭。于是左右适有衣紫而进者，公必曰：‘少却，吾恶紫臭。’”公曰：“诺。”于是日郎中莫衣紫，其明日国中莫衣紫，三日境内莫衣紫也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hwlym34","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hwlym34","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zhh1b1l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zhh1b1l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逢蒙学射于羿，尽羿之道，思天下惟羿为愈己，于是杀羿。孟子曰：“是亦羿有罪焉。”公明仪曰：“宜若无罪焉。”曰：“薄乎云尔，恶得无罪？郑人使子濯孺子侵卫，卫得庾公之斯追之。子濯孺子曰：‘今日我疾作，不可以执弓，吾死矣夫！’问其仆曰：‘追我者谁也？’其仆曰：‘庾公之斯也。’曰：‘吾生矣。’其仆曰：‘庾公之斯，卫之善射者也。夫子曰“吾生”，何谓也？’曰‘庾公之斯学射于尹公之他，尹公之他学射于我，夫尹公之他，端人也，其取友必端矣。’庾公之斯至，曰：‘夫子何为不执弓？’曰：‘今日我疾作，不可以执弓。’曰：‘小人学射于尹公之他，尹公之他学射于夫子，我不忍以夫子之道反害夫子。虽然，今日之事，君事也，我不敢废。抽矢叩轮，去其金，发乘矢而后反。’”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-q1kikqh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-q1kikqh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-r5l00x4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-r5l00x4","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"伯夷叔齐，孤竹君之二子也。父欲立叔齐，及父卒，叔齐让伯夷。伯夷曰：“父命也。”遂逃去。叔齐亦不肯立而逃之。国人立其中子。于是伯夷叔齐闻西伯昌善养老，盍往归焉。及至，西伯卒。武王载木主，号为文王，东伐纣。伯夷叔齐叩马而谏曰：“父死不葬，爰及干戈，可谓孝乎？以臣弑君，可谓仁乎？”左右欲兵之。太公曰：“此义人也。”扶而去之。武王已平殷乱，天下宗周，而伯夷叔齐耻之，义不食周粟，隐于首阳山，采薇而食之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-w96j0up","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w96j0up","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-wbsf26v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-wbsf26v","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人有卖骏马者，比三旦立于市，人莫知之。往见伯乐曰：“臣有骏马，欲卖之，比三旦立于市，人莫与言，愿子还而视之。去而顾之，臣请献一朝之贾。”伯乐乃还而视之，去而顾之，一旦而马价十倍。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-srremt1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-srremt1","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-w4xszem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-w4xszem","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多闻阙疑，慎言其余，则寡尤；多见阙殆，慎行其余，则寡悔。言寡尤，行寡悔，禄在其中矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-347kvkz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-347kvkz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7njstgp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7njstgp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"孔子适郑，与弟子相失，孔子独立郭东门。郑人或谓子贡曰：“东门有人，其颡似尧，其项类皋陶，其肩类子产，然自要以下不及禹三寸，累累若丧家之狗。”子贡以实告孔子。孔子欣然笑曰：“形状，末也。而谓似丧家之狗，然哉！然哉！”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-kjh0kfk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kjh0kfk","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-zbyuhis","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-zbyuhis","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"孔子晚而喜《易》，序《彖》、《系》、《象》、《说卦》、《文言》。读《易》，韦编三绝。曰：“假我数年，若是，我于《易》则彬彬矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-cp2c7a8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cp2c7a8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-miappa7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-miappa7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叔孙武叔语大夫于朝曰：“子贡贤于仲尼。” 子服景伯以告子贡。 子贡曰：“譬之宫墙，赐之墙也及肩，窥见室家之好。夫子之墙数仞，不得其门而入，不见宗庙之美，百官之富。得其门者或寡矣。夫子之云，不亦宜乎！”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-skgs4qm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-skgs4qm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-9ucpuvb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9ucpuvb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"齐桓公读书于堂上。轮扁斫轮于堂下，释椎凿而上，问桓公曰：“敢问，公之所读者何言邪？”公曰：“圣人之言也。”曰：“圣人在乎？”公曰：“已死矣。”曰：“然则君之所读者，古人之糟魄已夫？”桓公曰：“寡人读书，轮人安得议乎！有说则可，无说则死。”轮扁曰：“臣也从臣之事观之。斫轮，徐则甘而不固，疾则苦而不入。不徐不疾，得之于手而应于心，口不能言，有数存焉于其间。臣不能以喻臣之子，臣之子亦不能受之于臣，是以行年七十而老斫轮。古之人与其不可传也死矣，然则君之所读者，古人之糟魄已夫！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m20m4gl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m20m4gl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-ezptn24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ezptn24","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"厉王虐，国人谤王。召公告曰：“民不堪命矣！”王怒，得卫巫使监谤者，以告则杀之。国人莫敢言，道路以目。王喜，告召公曰：“吾能弭谤矣，乃不敢言。”召公曰：“是障之也。防民之口，甚于防川。川壅而溃，伤人必多，民亦如之。是故为川者，决之使导；为民者，宣之使言。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-1dhrmud","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-1dhrmud","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mdxdvhp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mdxdvhp","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公输子削竹木以为鹊，成而飞之，三日不下，公输子自以为至巧。子墨子谓公输子曰：“子之为鹊也，不如匠之为车辖。须臾斫三寸之木，而任五十石之重。故所为功，利于人谓之巧，不利于人谓之拙。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-067j7xg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-067j7xg","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-isvzd7u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-isvzd7u","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"齐桓公见小臣稷，一日三至，弗得见。从者曰：“万乘之主，见布衣之士，一日三至，而弗得见，亦可以止矣！”桓公曰：“不然。士骜禄爵者，固轻其主；其主骜霸者，亦轻其士。纵夫子骜禄爵，吾庸敢骜霸王乎？”遂见之不可止。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-lo92zex","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-lo92zex","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-k74i0wh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k74i0wh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"范蠡既雪会稽之耻，乃喟然而叹曰：“计然之策七，越用其五而得意。既已施于国，吾欲用之家。”乃乘扁舟浮于江湖，变名易姓，适齐为鸱夷子皮，之陶为朱公。朱公以为陶天下之中，诸侯四通，货物所交易也。乃治产积居，与时逐而不责于人。故善治生者，能择人而任时。十九年之中三致千金。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-hheyzyh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-hheyzyh","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-rgwhx3b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-rgwhx3b","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子夏之晋，过卫，有读史记者曰：“晋师三豕涉河。”子夏曰：“非也，是己亥也。夫已与三相近，豕与亥相似。”至于晋而问之，则曰：“晋师己亥涉河也。”辞多类非而是，多类是而非。是非之经，不可不分。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9m0qfjn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9m0qfjn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-4db1od6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4db1od6","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子夏过曾子。曾子曰：“入食。”子夏曰：“不为公费乎？”曾子曰：“君子有三费，饮食不在其中；君子有三乐，钟磬琴瑟不在其中。”子夏曰：“敢问三乐？”曾子曰：“有亲可畏，有君可事，有子可遗，此一乐也。有亲可谏，有君可去，有子可怒，此二乐也。有君可喻，有友可助，此三乐也。”子夏问：“敢问三费？”曾子曰：“少而学，长而忘，此一费也。事君有功，而轻负之，此二费也，久交友而中绝之，此三费也。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ehm5bbr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ehm5bbr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-mdpxjfa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-mdpxjfa","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔秦伯嫁其女于晋公子，令晋为之饰装，从衣文之媵七十人。至晋，晋人爱其妾而贱公女。此可谓善嫁妾，而未可谓善嫁女也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qg0vrt2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qg0vrt2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-huk6zew","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-huk6zew","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔者曾子处费，费人有与曾子同名族者而杀人。人告曾子母曰：“曾参杀人。”曾子之母曰：“吾子不杀人。”织自若。有顷焉，人又曰：“曾参杀人。”其母尚织自若也。顷之，一人又告之曰：“曾参杀人。”其母惧，投杼逾墙而走。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-235pnhs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-235pnhs","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-7v5yonf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-7v5yonf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"范蠡遂去，自齐遗大夫种书曰：“飞鸟尽，良弓藏；狡兔死，走狗烹。越王为人长颈鸟喙，可与共患难，不可与共乐。子何不去？”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-4zf05f0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-4zf05f0","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-8269ugx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-8269ugx","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"禽子问曰：多言有益乎？墨子曰：虾蟆、蛙黾，日夜恒鸣，口干舌擗，然而不听。今观晨鸡，时夜而鸣，天下振动。多言何益？唯其言之时也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-prw67mb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-prw67mb","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-41p7naf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-41p7naf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巫马子谓子墨子曰：\"子兼爱天下，未云利也，我不爱天下，未云贼也。功皆未至，子何独自是而非我哉？”子墨子曰：今有燎者于此，一人奉水将灌之，一人掺火将益之，功皆未至，子何贵于二人？”巫马子曰：我是彼奉水者之意，而非夫掺火者之意。”子墨子曰：\"吾亦是吾意而非子之意也。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-35m94va","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-35m94va","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-unga1rz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-unga1rz","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叶公问孔子于子路，子路不对。子曰：“女奚不曰：其为人也，发愤忘食，乐以忘忧，不知老之将至云尔。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fmm1zog","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fmm1zog","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-cnkd5c2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-cnkd5c2","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子路日:““伤哉贫也!生无以养，死无以葬。”子曰:“啜菽饮水，孝也。”"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-07g9mmv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-07g9mmv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-b8p5q5l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-b8p5q5l","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"生活不仅有田园与诗，更有眼前的苟且。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-9x865r3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-9x865r3","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-saqe3mn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-saqe3mn","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子曰：“后生可畏，焉知来者之不如今也？四十、五十而无闻焉，斯亦不足畏也已。”"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-k34jwli","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-k34jwli","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-d9b6ise","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-d9b6ise","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"融合方式要如盐溶于水般不着痕迹，可采用语录式题记、巧妙化用意象、隐喻重构等方式。严禁为了炫技而生搬硬套、强行堆砌，确保古典元素与现代文思共生共振，而非逻辑割裂。名言与典故必须作为论据服务于论点，不得为了展示库存而强行插入。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-ou0bpmf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"OC4=","Num":8},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-ou0bpmf","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-75r52u8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-75r52u8","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"篇幅"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：请严格控制在850字左右，结尾必须留有2-3句极具力量的金句进行收束，不得草率。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-m2o9fwc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"OS4=","Num":9},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-m2o9fwc","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-kp43q1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-kp43q1c","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"输出格式"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-c2vsxei","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-c2vsxei","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-s2174jl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-s2174jl","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-251yrut","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-251yrut","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"标题（居中，力求新颖、吸睛）"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-5oy210n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-5oy210n","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-tq92nxr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-tq92nxr","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"正文（分段清晰，每段首行缩进两字符）"}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-akvykl7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-akvykl7","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"【作文题目/材料/原文】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n（在此处粘贴具体的作文题目、材料或话题，例如：2025年全国一卷关于老舍、艾青、穆旦的材料……）"}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-vq8bnak","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-vq8bnak","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"【逻辑自检与优化指令】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n在生成完正文后，请严格执行以下检查步骤，以确保文章的逻辑严密性和考场适用性："}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-0wuyper","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-0wuyper","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-19nqvgm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-19nqvgm","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逻辑回溯：请审视全文的论证链条。是否存在“观点A -\u003e 论据B（其实不支持A）”的逻辑断裂？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-qluio2d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-qluio2d","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-x29zj7h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-x29zj7h","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"隐喻准确性检查（重点）：请检查文中关于“熵增定律”的隐喻（或其他科学原理/心理学效应）是否准确？它是否真正支撑了“自律”或“对抗无序”这一分论点，还是仅仅是一个华丽的辞藻堆砌？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-apjak0j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-apjak0j","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-e3vaaea","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-e3vaaea","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"素材去重与更新：检查文中是否误用了“司马迁、李白、爱迪生”等过度使用的陈词滥调？如果是，请替换为更具时代感的素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260603095040-fa7vt92","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-fa7vt92","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260603095040-uft8lnv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260603095040-uft8lnv","updated":"20260603095040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"阅卷视角模拟：如果你是一位拥有20年经验的高考阅卷老师，这篇文章最可能因为什么被扣分（如：偏题、结构混乱、矫情）？请指出并微调。"}]}]}]}]}